var book = {
	"name": "Job",
	"numChapters": 42,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>There was a man in the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12871A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12871A\"></sup>Uz whose name was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12871B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12871B\"></sup>Job, and that man was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12871C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12871C\"></sup>blameless and upright, one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12871D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12871D\"></sup>feared God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12871E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12871E\"></sup>turned away from evil.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>There were born to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12872F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12872F\"></sup>seven sons and three daughters.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He possessed 7,000 sheep, 3,000 camels, 500 yoke of oxen, and 500 female donkeys, and very many servants, so that this man was the greatest of all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12873G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12873G\"></sup>the people of the east.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>His sons used to go and hold a feast in the house of each one on his day, and they would send and invite their three sisters to eat and drink with them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And when the days of the feast had run their course, Job would send and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12875H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12875H\"></sup>consecrate them, and he would rise early in the morning and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12875I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12875I\"></sup>offer burnt offerings according to the number of them all. For Job said, “It may be that my children have sinned, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12875J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12875J\"></sup>cursed God in their hearts.” Thus Job did continually.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now there was a day when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12876K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12876K\"></sup>the sons of God came to present themselves before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12876L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12876L\"></sup>Satan also came among them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “From where have you come?” Satan answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said, “From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12877M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12877M\"></sup>going to and fro on the earth, and from walking up and down on it.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12878N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12878N\"></sup>considered my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12878O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12878O\"></sup>servant Job, that there is none like him on the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12878P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12878P\"></sup>a blameless and upright man, who fears God and turns away from evil?”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then Satan answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said, “Does Job fear God for no reason?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Have you not put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12880Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12880Q\"></sup>a hedge around him and his house and all that he has, on every side? You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12880R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12880R\"></sup>blessed the work of his hands, and his possessions have increased in the land.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12881S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12881S\"></sup>stretch out your hand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12881T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12881T\"></sup>touch all that he has, and he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12881U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12881U\"></sup>curse you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12881V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12881V\"></sup>to your face.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Behold, all that he has is in your hand. Only against him do not stretch out your hand.” So Satan went out from the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now there was a day when his sons and daughters were eating and drinking wine in their oldest brother's house,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and there came a messenger to Job and said, “The oxen were plowing and the donkeys feeding beside them,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12885W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12885W\"></sup>the Sabeans fell upon them and took them and struck down the servants with the edge of the sword, and I alone have escaped to tell you.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>While he was yet speaking, there came another and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12886X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12886X\"></sup>“The fire of God fell from heaven and burned up the sheep and the servants and consumed them, and I alone have escaped to tell you.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>While he was yet speaking, there came another and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12887Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12887Y\"></sup>“The Chaldeans formed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12887Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12887Z\"></sup>three groups and made a raid on the camels and took them and struck down the servants with the edge of the sword, and I alone have escaped to tell you.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>While he was yet speaking, there came another and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12888AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12888AA\"></sup>“Your sons and daughters were eating and drinking wine in their oldest brother's house,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and behold, a great wind came across <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12889AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12889AB\"></sup>the wilderness and struck the four corners of the house, and it fell upon the young people, and they are dead, and I alone have escaped to tell you.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then Job arose and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12890AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12890AC\"></sup>tore his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12890AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12890AD\"></sup>robe and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12890AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12890AE\"></sup>shaved his head <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12890AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12890AF\"></sup>and fell on the ground and worshiped.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12891AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12891AG\"></sup>“Naked I came from my mother's womb, and naked shall I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12891AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12891AH\"></sup>return. The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12891AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12891AI\"></sup>gave, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has taken away; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12891AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12891AJ\"></sup>blessed be the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12892AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12892AK\"></sup>In all this Job did not sin or charge God with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12892AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12892AL\"></sup>wrong."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12893A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12893A\"></sup>there was a day when the sons of God came to present themselves before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and Satan also came among them to present himself before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “From where have you come?” Satan answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said, “From going to and fro on the earth, and from walking up and down on it.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Have you considered my servant Job, that there is none like him on the earth, a blameless and upright man, who fears God and turns away from evil? He still <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12895B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12895B\"></sup>holds fast his integrity, although you incited me against him to destroy him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12895C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12895C\"></sup>without reason.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then Satan answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said, “Skin for skin! All that a man has he will give for his life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12897D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12897D\"></sup>stretch out your hand and touch his bone and his flesh, and he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12897E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12897E\"></sup>curse you to your face.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Behold, he is in your hand; only spare his life.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So Satan went out from the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and struck Job with loathsome <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12899F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12899F\"></sup>sores from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12899G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12899G\"></sup>the sole of his foot to the crown of his head.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And he took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12900H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12900H\"></sup>a piece of broken pottery with which to scrape himself while he sat in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12900I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12900I\"></sup>the ashes.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then his wife said to him, “Do you still <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12901J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12901J\"></sup>hold fast your integrity? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12901K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12901K\"></sup>Curse God and die.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But he said to her, “You speak as one of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12902L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12902L\"></sup>foolish women would speak. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12902M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12902M\"></sup>Shall we receive good from God, and shall we not receive evil?” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12902N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12902N\"></sup>In all this Job did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12902O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12902O\"></sup>sin with his lips.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now when Job's three <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12903P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12903P\"></sup>friends heard of all this evil that had come upon him, they came each from his own place, Eliphaz <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12903Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12903Q\"></sup>the Temanite, Bildad <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12903R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12903R\"></sup>the Shuhite, and Zophar the Naamathite. They made an appointment together to come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12903S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12903S\"></sup>show him sympathy and comfort him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And when they saw him from a distance, they did not recognize him. And they raised their voices and wept, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12904T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12904T\"></sup>tore their robes and sprinkled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12904U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12904U\"></sup>dust on their heads toward heaven.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And they sat with him on the ground <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12905V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12905V\"></sup>seven days and seven nights, and no one spoke a word to him, for they saw that his suffering was very great."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>After this Job <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12906A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12906A\"></sup>opened his mouth and cursed the day of his birth.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And Job said:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12908B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12908B\"></sup>“Let the day perish on which I was born,and the night that said,‘A man is conceived.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Let that day be darkness!May God above not seek it,nor light shine upon it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Let gloom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12910C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12910C\"></sup>deep darkness claim it.Let clouds dwell upon it;let the blackness of the day terrify it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>That night—let thick darkness seize it!Let it not rejoice among the days of the year;let it not come into the number of the months.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Behold, let that night be barren;let no joyful cry enter it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Let those curse it who curse the day,who are ready to rouse up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12913D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12913D\"></sup>Leviathan.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Let the stars of its dawn be dark;let it hope for light, but have none,nor see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12914E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12914E\"></sup>the eyelids of the morning,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>because it did not shut the doors of my mother's womb,nor hide trouble from my eyes.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12916F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12916F\"></sup>did I not die at birth,come out from the womb and expire?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Why did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12917G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12917G\"></sup>the knees receive me?Or why the breasts, that I should nurse?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For then I would have lain down and been quiet;I would have slept; then I would have been at rest,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>with kings and counselors of the earthwho <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12919H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12919H\"></sup>rebuilt ruins for themselves,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>or with princes who had gold,who filled their houses with silver.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Or why was I not as a hidden <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12921I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12921I\"></sup>stillborn child,as infants who never see the light?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>There the wicked cease from troubling,and there the weary are at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12922J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12922J\"></sup>rest.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>There the prisoners are at ease together;they hear not the voice of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12923K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12923K\"></sup>the taskmaster.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The small and the great are there,and the slave is free from his master.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Why is light given to him who is in misery,and life to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12925L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12925L\"></sup>the bitter in soul,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12926M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12926M\"></sup>long for death, but it comes not,and dig for it more than for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12926N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12926N\"></sup>hidden treasures,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>who rejoice exceedinglyand are glad when they find the grave?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Why is light given to a man whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12928O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12928O\"></sup>way is hidden,whom God has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12928P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12928P\"></sup>hedged in?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For my sighing comes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12929Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12929Q\"></sup>instead of my bread,and my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12929R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12929R\"></sup>groanings are poured out like water.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12930S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12930S\"></sup>For the thing that I fear comes upon me,and what I dread befalls me.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I am not at ease, nor am I quiet;I have no rest, but trouble comes.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Then Eliphaz the Temanite answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“If one ventures a word with you, will you be impatient?Yet who can keep from speaking?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Behold, you have instructed many,and you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12934A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12934A\"></sup>strengthened the weak hands.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your words have upheld him who was stumbling,and you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12935B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12935B\"></sup>made firm the feeble knees.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But now it has come to you, and you are impatient;it touches you, and you are dismayed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12937C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12937C\"></sup>Is not your fear of God your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12937D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12937D\"></sup>confidence,and the integrity of your ways your hope?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Remember: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12938E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12938E\"></sup>who that was innocent ever perished?Or where were the upright cut off?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>As I have seen, those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12939F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12939F\"></sup>plow iniquityand sow trouble reap the same.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>By <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12940G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12940G\"></sup>the breath of God they perish,and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12940H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12940H\"></sup>the blast of his anger they are consumed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The roar of the lion, the voice of the fierce lion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12941I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12941I\"></sup>the teeth of the young lions are broken.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The strong lion perishes for lack of prey,and the cubs of the lioness are scattered.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Now a word was brought to me stealthily;my ear received <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12943J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12943J\"></sup>the whisper of it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Amid <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12944K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12944K\"></sup>thoughts from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12944L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12944L\"></sup>visions of the night,when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12944M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12944M\"></sup>deep sleep falls on men,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>dread came upon me, and trembling,which made all my bones shake.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>A spirit glided past my face;the hair of my flesh stood up.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>It stood still,but I could not discern its appearance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12947N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12947N\"></sup>A form was before my eyes;there was silence, then I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12947O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12947O\"></sup>a voice:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12948P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12948P\"></sup>‘Can mortal man be in the right before God?Can a man be pure before his Maker?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Even in his servants <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12949Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12949Q\"></sup>he puts no trust,and his angels he charges with error;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>how much more those who dwell in houses of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12950R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12950R\"></sup>clay,whose foundation is in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12950S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12950S\"></sup>the dust,who are crushed like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12950T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12950T\"></sup>the moth.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Between <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12951U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12951U\"></sup>morning and evening they are beaten to pieces;they perish forever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12951V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12951V\"></sup>without anyone regarding it.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Is not their tent-cord plucked up within them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12952W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12952W\"></sup>do they not die, and that without wisdom?’"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>“Call now; is there anyone who will answer you?To which of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12953A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12953A\"></sup>the holy ones will you turn?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Surely vexation kills the fool,and jealousy slays the simple.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12955B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12955B\"></sup>I have seen the fool taking root,but suddenly I cursed his dwelling.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>His children are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12956C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12956C\"></sup>far from safety;they are crushed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12956D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12956D\"></sup>the gate,and there is no one to deliver them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The hungry eat his harvest,and he takes it even out of thorns,and the thirsty pant after his wealth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For affliction does not come from the dust,nor does trouble sprout from the ground,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>but man is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12959E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12959E\"></sup>born to troubleas the sparks fly upward.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“As for me, I would seek God,and to God would I commit my cause,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12961F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12961F\"></sup>does great things and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12961G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12961G\"></sup>unsearchable,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12961H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12961H\"></sup>marvelous things without number:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>he gives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12962I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12962I\"></sup>rain on the earthand sends waters on the fields;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12963J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12963J\"></sup>sets on high those who are lowly,and those who mourn are lifted to safety.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12964K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12964K\"></sup>frustrates the devices of the crafty,so that their hands achieve no success.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12965L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12965L\"></sup>catches the wise in their own craftiness,and the schemes of the wily are brought to a quick end.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They meet with darkness in the daytimeand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12966M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12966M\"></sup>grope at noonday as in the night.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12967N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12967N\"></sup>saves the needy from the sword of their mouthand from the hand of the mighty.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So the poor have hope,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12968O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12968O\"></sup>injustice shuts her mouth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12969P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12969P\"></sup>blessed is the one whom God reproves;therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12969Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12969Q\"></sup>despise not the discipline of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12969R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12969R\"></sup>Almighty.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For he wounds, but he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12970S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12970S\"></sup>binds up;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12970T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12970T\"></sup>shatters, but his hands heal.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12971U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12971U\"></sup>deliver you from six troubles;in seven no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12971V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12971V\"></sup>evil shall touch you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12972W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12972W\"></sup>In famine he will redeem you from death,and in war from the power of the sword.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12973X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12973X\"></sup>hidden from the lash of the tongue,and shall not fear destruction when it comes.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>At destruction and famine you shall laugh,and shall not fear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12974Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12974Y\"></sup>the beasts of the earth.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For you shall be in league with the stones of the field,and the beasts of the field shall be at peace with you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>You shall know that your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12976Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12976Z\"></sup>tent is at peace,and you shall inspect your fold and miss nothing.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>You shall know also that your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12977AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12977AA\"></sup>offspring shall be many,and your descendants as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12977AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12977AB\"></sup>the grass of the earth.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You shall come to your grave in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12978AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12978AC\"></sup>ripe old age,like a sheaf gathered up in its season.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Behold, this we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12979AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12979AD\"></sup>searched out; it is true.Hear, and know it for your good.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Then Job answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Oh that my vexation were weighed,and all my calamity laid in the balances!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For then it would be heavier than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12982A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12982A\"></sup>the sand of the sea;therefore my words have been rash.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12983B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12983B\"></sup>the arrows of the Almighty are in me;my spirit drinks their poison;the terrors of God are arrayed against me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Does the wild donkey bray when he has grass,or the ox low over his fodder?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Can that which is tasteless be eaten without salt,or is there any taste in the juice of the mallow?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>My appetite refuses to touch them;they are as food that is loathsome to me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Oh that I might have my request,and that God would fulfill my hope,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>that it would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12988C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12988C\"></sup>please God to crush me,that he would let loose his hand and cut me off!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This would be my comfort;I would even exult in pain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12989D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12989D\"></sup>unsparing,for I have not denied the words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12989E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12989E\"></sup>the Holy One.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>What is my strength, that I should wait?And what is my end, that I should be patient?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Is my strength the strength of stones, or is my flesh bronze?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Have I any help in me,when resource is driven from me?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12993F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12993F\"></sup>withholds kindness from a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12993G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12993G\"></sup>friendforsakes the fear of the Almighty.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12994H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12994H\"></sup>brothers are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12994I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12994I\"></sup>treacherous as a torrent-bed,as torrential <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12994J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12994J\"></sup>streams that pass away,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>which are dark with ice,and where the snow hides itself.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>When they melt, they disappear;when it is hot, they vanish from their place.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The caravans turn aside from their course;they go up into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12997K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12997K\"></sup>the waste and perish.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The caravans of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12998L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12998L\"></sup>Tema look,the travelers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12998M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12998M\"></sup>Sheba hope.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12999N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12999N\"></sup>ashamed because they were confident;they come there and are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-12999O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-12999O\"></sup>disappointed.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For you have now become nothing;you see my calamity and are afraid.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Have I said, ‘Make me a gift’?Or, ‘From your wealth offer a bribe for me’?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Or, ‘Deliver me from the adversary's hand’?Or, ‘Redeem me from the hand of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13002P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13002P\"></sup>the ruthless’?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Teach me, and I will be silent;make me understand how I have gone astray.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>How forceful are upright words!But what does reproof from you reprove?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Do you think that you can reprove words,when the speech of a despairing man is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13005Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13005Q\"></sup>wind?",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>You would even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13006R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13006R\"></sup>cast lots over the fatherless,and bargain over your friend.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“But now, be pleased to look at me,for I will not lie to your face.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13008S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13008S\"></sup>Please turn; let no injustice be done.Turn now; my vindication is at stake.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Is there any injustice on my tongue?Cannot my palate discern the cause of calamity?"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>“Has not man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13010A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13010A\"></sup>a hard service on earth,and are not his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13010B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13010B\"></sup>days like the days of a hired hand?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Like a slave who longs for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13011C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13011C\"></sup>the shadow,and like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13011D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13011D\"></sup>a hired hand who looks for his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13011E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13011E\"></sup>wages,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>so I am allotted months of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13012F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13012F\"></sup>emptiness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13012G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13012G\"></sup>and nights of misery are apportioned to me.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13013H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13013H\"></sup>When I lie down I say, ‘When shall I arise?’But the night is long,and I am full of tossing till the dawn.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>My flesh is clothed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13014I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13014I\"></sup>worms and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13014J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13014J\"></sup>dirt;my skin hardens, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13014K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13014K\"></sup>breaks out afresh.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>My days are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13015L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13015L\"></sup>swifter than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13015M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13015M\"></sup>a weaver's shuttleand come to their end without hope.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Remember that my life is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13016N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13016N\"></sup>breath;my eye will never again see good.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13017O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13017O\"></sup>The eye of him who sees me will behold me no more;while your eyes are on me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13017P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13017P\"></sup>I shall be gone.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13018Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13018Q\"></sup>the cloud fades and vanishes,so he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13018R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13018R\"></sup>goes down to Sheol does not come up;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13019S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13019S\"></sup>returns no more to his house,nor does his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13019T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13019T\"></sup>place know him anymore.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Therefore I will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13020U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13020U\"></sup>restrain my mouth;I will speak in the anguish of my spirit;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13020V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13020V\"></sup>complain in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13020W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13020W\"></sup>the bitterness of my soul.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Am I the sea, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13021X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13021X\"></sup>a sea monster,that you set a guard over me?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13022Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13022Y\"></sup>When I say, ‘My bed will comfort me,my couch will ease my complaint,’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>then you scare me with dreamsand terrify me with visions,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>so that I would choose stranglingand death rather than my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13024Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13024Z\"></sup>bones.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13025AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13025AA\"></sup>loathe my life; I would not live forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13025AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13025AB\"></sup>Leave me alone, for my days are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13025AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13025AC\"></sup>a breath.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13026AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13026AD\"></sup>What is man, that you make so much of him,and that you set your heart on him,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13027AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13027AE\"></sup>visit him every morningand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13027AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13027AF\"></sup>test him every moment?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>How long will you not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13028AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13028AG\"></sup>look away from me,nor leave me alone till I swallow my spit?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>If I sin, what do I do to you, you watcher of mankind?Why have you made me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13029AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13029AH\"></sup>your mark?Why have I become a burden to you?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Why do you not pardon my transgressionand take away my iniquity?For now I shall lie in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13030AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13030AI\"></sup>the earth;you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13030AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13030AJ\"></sup>seek me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13030AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13030AK\"></sup>but I shall not be.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13031A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13031A\"></sup>Bildad the Shuhite answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How long will you say these things,and the words of your mouth be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13032B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13032B\"></sup>great wind?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13033C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13033C\"></sup>Does God pervert justice?Or does the Almighty pervert the right?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>If your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13034D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13034D\"></sup>children have sinned against him,he has delivered them into the hand of their transgression.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If you will seek Godand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13035E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13035E\"></sup>plead with the Almighty for mercy,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>if you are pure and upright,surely then he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13036F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13036F\"></sup>rouse himself for youand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13036G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13036G\"></sup>restore your rightful habitation.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And though your beginning was small,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13037H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13037H\"></sup>your latter days will be very great.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13038I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13038I\"></sup>inquire, please, of bygone ages,and consider what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13038J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13038J\"></sup>the fathers have searched out.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For we are but of yesterday and know nothing,for our days on earth are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13039K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13039K\"></sup>a shadow.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Will they not teach you and tell youand utter words out of their understanding?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Can papyrus grow where there is no marsh?Can reeds flourish where there is no water?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>While yet in flower and not cut down,they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13042L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13042L\"></sup>wither before any other plant.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Such are the paths of all who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13043M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13043M\"></sup>forget God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13043N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13043N\"></sup>the hope of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13043O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13043O\"></sup>the godless shall perish.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>His confidence is severed,and his trust is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13044P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13044P\"></sup>a spider's web.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He leans against his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13045Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13045Q\"></sup>house, but it does not stand;he lays hold of it, but it does not endure.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He is a lush plant before the sun,and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13046R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13046R\"></sup>shoots spread over his garden.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>His roots entwine the stone heap;he looks upon a house of stones.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If he is destroyed from his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13048S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13048S\"></sup>place,then it will deny him, saying, ‘I have never <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13048T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13048T\"></sup>seen you.’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Behold, this is the joy of his way,and out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13049U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13049U\"></sup>the soil others will spring.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Behold, God will not reject a blameless man,nor take the hand of evildoers.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He will yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13051V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13051V\"></sup>fill your mouth with laughter,and your lips with shouting.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Those who hate you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13052W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13052W\"></sup>clothed with shame,and the tent of the wicked will be no more.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Then Job answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Truly I know that it is so:But how can a man be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13054A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13054A\"></sup>in the right before God?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If one wished to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13055B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13055B\"></sup>contend with him,one could not answer him once in a thousand times.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13056C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13056C\"></sup>wise in heart and mighty in strength—who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13056D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13056D\"></sup>hardened himself against him, and succeeded?—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>he who removes mountains, and they know it not,when he overturns them in his anger,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13058E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13058E\"></sup>shakes the earth out of its place,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13058F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13058F\"></sup>its pillars tremble;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>who commands the sun, and it does not rise;who seals up the stars;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>who alone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13060G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13060G\"></sup>stretched out the heavensand trampled the waves of the sea;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13061H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13061H\"></sup>made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13061I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13061I\"></sup>the Bear and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13061J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13061J\"></sup>Orion,the Pleiades <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13061K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13061K\"></sup>and the chambers of the south;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>who does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13062L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13062L\"></sup>great things beyond searching out,and marvelous things beyond number.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Behold, he passes by me, and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13063M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13063M\"></sup>see him not;he moves on, but I do not perceive him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Behold, he snatches away; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13064N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13064N\"></sup>who can turn him back?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13064O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13064O\"></sup>Who will say to him, ‘What are you doing?’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“God will not turn back his anger;beneath him bowed the helpers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13065P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13065P\"></sup>Rahab.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13066Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13066Q\"></sup>How then can I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13066R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13066R\"></sup>answer him,choosing my words with him?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13067S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13067S\"></sup>Though I am in the right, I cannot answer him;I must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13067T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13067T\"></sup>appeal for mercy to my accuser.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If I summoned him and he answered me,I would not believe that he was listening to my voice.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For he crushes me with a tempestand multiplies my wounds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13069U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13069U\"></sup>without cause;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>he will not let me get my breath,but fills me with bitterness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If it is a contest of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13071V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13071V\"></sup>strength, behold, he is mighty!If it is a matter of justice, who can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13071W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13071W\"></sup>summon him?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Though I am in the right, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13072X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13072X\"></sup>my own mouth would condemn me;though I am blameless, he would prove me perverse.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13073Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13073Y\"></sup>blameless; I regard not myself;I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13073Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13073Z\"></sup>loathe my life.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>It is all one; therefore I say,‘He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13074AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13074AA\"></sup>destroys both the blameless and the wicked.’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13075AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13075AB\"></sup>disaster brings sudden death,he mocks at the calamity of the innocent.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13076AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13076AC\"></sup>The earth is given into the hand of the wicked;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13076AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13076AD\"></sup>covers the faces of its judges—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13076AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13076AE\"></sup>if it is not he, who then is it?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13077AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13077AF\"></sup>days are swifter than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13077AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13077AG\"></sup>a runner;they flee away; they see no good.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They go by like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13078AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13078AH\"></sup>skiffs of reed,like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13078AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13078AI\"></sup>an eagle swooping on the prey.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>If I say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13079AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13079AJ\"></sup>‘I will forget my complaint,I will put off my sad face, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13079AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13079AK\"></sup>be of good cheer,’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>I become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13080AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13080AL\"></sup>afraid of all my suffering,for I know you will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13080AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13080AM\"></sup>hold me innocent.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13081AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13081AN\"></sup>condemned;why then do I labor in vain?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>If I wash myself with snowand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13082AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13082AO\"></sup>cleanse my hands with lye,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>yet you will plunge me into a pit,and my own clothes will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13083AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13083AP\"></sup>abhor me.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For he is not a man, as I am, that I might answer him,that we should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13084AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13084AQ\"></sup>come to trial together.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13085AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13085AR\"></sup>There is no arbiter between us,who might lay his hand on us both.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13086AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13086AS\"></sup>Let him take his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13086AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13086AT\"></sup>rod away from me,and let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13086AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13086AU\"></sup>not dread of him terrify me.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Then I would speak without fear of him,for I am not so in myself."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13088A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13088A\"></sup>loathe my life;I will give free utterance to my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13088B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13088B\"></sup>complaint;I will speak in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13088C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13088C\"></sup>the bitterness of my soul.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will say to God, Do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13089D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13089D\"></sup>condemn me;let me know why you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13089E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13089E\"></sup>contend against me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13090F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13090F\"></sup>Does it seem good to you to oppress,to despise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13090G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13090G\"></sup>the work of your hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13090H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13090H\"></sup>and favor the designs of the wicked?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13091I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13091I\"></sup>eyes of flesh?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13091J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13091J\"></sup>Do you see as man sees?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Are your days as the days of man,or your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13092K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13092K\"></sup>years as a man's years,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13093L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13093L\"></sup>seek out my iniquityand search for my sin,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>although you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13094M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13094M\"></sup>know that I am not guilty,and there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13094N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13094N\"></sup>none to deliver out of your hand?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13095O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13095O\"></sup>Your hands fashioned and made me,and now you have destroyed me altogether.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Remember that you have made me like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13096P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13096P\"></sup>clay;and will you return me to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13096Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13096Q\"></sup>dust?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Did you not pour me out like milkand curdle me like cheese?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>You clothed me with skin and flesh,and knit me together with bones and sinews.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You have granted me life and steadfast love,and your care has preserved my spirit.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Yet these things you hid in your heart;I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13100R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13100R\"></sup>this was your purpose.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If I sin, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13101S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13101S\"></sup>watch meand do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13101T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13101T\"></sup>acquit me of my iniquity.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13102U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13102U\"></sup>If I am guilty, woe to me!If I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13102V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13102V\"></sup>in the right, I cannot lift up my head,for I am filled with disgraceand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13102W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13102W\"></sup>look on my affliction.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And were my head lifted up, you would hunt me like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13103X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13103X\"></sup>a lionand again work <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13103Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13103Y\"></sup>wonders against me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You renew your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13104Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13104Z\"></sup>witnesses against meand increase your vexation toward me;you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13104AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13104AA\"></sup>bring fresh troops against me.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13105AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13105AB\"></sup>“Why did you bring me out from the womb?Would that I had died before any eye had seen me",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13106AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13106AC\"></sup>and were as though I had not been,carried from the womb to the grave.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13107AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13107AD\"></sup>Are not my days few?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13107AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13107AE\"></sup>Then cease, and leave me alone, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13107AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13107AF\"></sup>that I may find a little cheer",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>before I go—and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13108AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13108AG\"></sup>I shall not return—to the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13108AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13108AH\"></sup>darkness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13108AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13108AI\"></sup>deep shadow,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>the land of gloom like thick darkness,like deep shadow without any order,where light is as thick darkness.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13110A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13110A\"></sup>Zophar the Naamathite answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13111B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13111B\"></sup>a multitude of words go unanswered,and a man full of talk be judged right?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Should your babble silence men,and when you mock, shall no one shame you?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13113C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13113C\"></sup>you say, ‘My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13113D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13113D\"></sup>doctrine is pure,and I am clean in God's eyes.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But oh, that God would speakand open his lips to you,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and that he would tell you the secrets of wisdom!For he is manifold in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13115E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13115E\"></sup>understanding.Know then that God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13115F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13115F\"></sup>exacts of you less than your guilt deserves.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13116G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13116G\"></sup>“Can you find out the deep things of God?Can you find out the limit of the Almighty?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13117H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13117H\"></sup>higher than heaven—what can you do?Deeper than Sheol—what can you know?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Its measure is longer than the earthand broader than the sea.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>If he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13119I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13119I\"></sup>passes through and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13119J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13119J\"></sup>imprisonsand summons the court, who can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13119K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13119K\"></sup>turn him back?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For he knows <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13120L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13120L\"></sup>worthless men;when he sees iniquity, will he not consider it?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But a stupid man will get understandingwhen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13121M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13121M\"></sup>a wild donkey's colt is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13121N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13121N\"></sup>born a man!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“If you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13122O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13122O\"></sup>prepare your heart,you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13122P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13122P\"></sup>stretch out your hands toward him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If iniquity is in your hand, put it far away,and let not injustice dwell in your tents.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Surely then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13124Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13124Q\"></sup>lift up your face without <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13124R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13124R\"></sup>blemish;you will be secure and will not fear.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13125S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13125S\"></sup>forget your misery;you will remember it as waters that have passed away.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And your life will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13126T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13126T\"></sup>brighter than the noonday;its darkness will be like the morning.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And you will feel secure, because there is hope;you will look around and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13127U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13127U\"></sup>take your rest in security.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13128V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13128V\"></sup>lie down, and none will make you afraid;many will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13128W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13128W\"></sup>court your favor.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13129X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13129X\"></sup>the eyes of the wicked will fail;all way of escape will be lost to them,and their hope is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13129Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13129Y\"></sup>to breathe their last.”"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Then Job answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“No doubt you are the people,and wisdom will die with you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13132A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13132A\"></sup>understanding as well as you;I am not inferior to you.Who does not know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13132B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13132B\"></sup>such things as these?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13133C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13133C\"></sup>a laughingstock to my friends;I, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13133D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13133D\"></sup>called to God and he answered me,a just and blameless man, am a laughingstock.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>In the thought of one who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13134E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13134E\"></sup>at ease there is contempt for misfortune;it is ready for those whose feet slip.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13135F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13135F\"></sup>The tents of robbers are at peace,and those who provoke God are secure,who bring their god in their hand.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“But ask the beasts, and they will teach you;the birds of the heavens, and they will tell you;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>or the bushes of the earth, and they will teach you;and the fish of the sea will declare to you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Who among all these does not knowthat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13138G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13138G\"></sup>the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done this?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13139H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13139H\"></sup>his hand is the life of every living thingand the breath of all mankind.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13140I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13140I\"></sup>the ear test wordsas the palate tastes food?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Wisdom is with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13141J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13141J\"></sup>the aged,and understanding in length of days.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13142K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13142K\"></sup>“With God are wisdom and might;he has counsel and understanding.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If he tears down, none can rebuild;if he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13143L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13143L\"></sup>shuts a man in, none can open.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13144M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13144M\"></sup>withholds the waters, they dry up;if he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13144N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13144N\"></sup>sends them out, they overwhelm the land.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>With him are strength and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13145O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13145O\"></sup>sound wisdom;the deceived and the deceiver are his.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He leads <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13146P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13146P\"></sup>counselors away stripped,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13146Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13146Q\"></sup>judges he makes fools.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13147R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13147R\"></sup>looses the bonds of kingsand binds a waistcloth on their hips.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He leads priests away strippedand overthrows the mighty.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He deprives of speech those who are trusted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13149S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13149S\"></sup>and takes away the discernment of the elders.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13150T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13150T\"></sup>pours contempt on princesand loosens the belt of the strong.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13151U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13151U\"></sup>uncovers the deeps out of darknessand brings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13151V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13151V\"></sup>deep darkness to light.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13152W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13152W\"></sup>makes nations great, and he destroys them;he enlarges nations, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13152X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13152X\"></sup>leads them away.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He takes away understanding from the chiefs of the people of the earthand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13153Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13153Y\"></sup>makes them wander in a trackless waste.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13154Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13154Z\"></sup>grope in the dark without light,and he makes them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13154AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13154AA\"></sup>stagger like a drunken man."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>“Behold, my eye has seen all this,my ear has heard and understood it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13156A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13156A\"></sup>What you know, I also know;I am not inferior to you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13157B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13157B\"></sup>But I would speak to the Almighty,and I desire to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13157C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13157C\"></sup>argue my case with God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>As for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13158D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13158D\"></sup>you whitewash with lies;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13158E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13158E\"></sup>worthless physicians are you all.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Oh that you would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13159F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13159F\"></sup>keep silent,and it would be your wisdom!",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Hear now my argumentand listen to the pleadings of my lips.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13161G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13161G\"></sup>speak falsely for Godand speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13161H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13161H\"></sup>deceitfully for him?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Will you show partiality toward him?Will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13162I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13162I\"></sup>plead the case for God?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Will it be well with you when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13163J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13163J\"></sup>searches you out?Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13163K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13163K\"></sup>can you deceive him, as one deceives a man?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He will surely rebuke youif in secret you show partiality.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Will not his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13165L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13165L\"></sup>majesty terrify you,and the dread of him fall upon you?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Your maxims are proverbs of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13166M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13166M\"></sup>ashes;your defenses are defenses of clay.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Let me have silence, and I will speak,and let come on me what may.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Why should I take my flesh in my teethand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13168N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13168N\"></sup>put my life in my hand?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13169O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13169O\"></sup>Though he slay me, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13169P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13169P\"></sup>hope in him;yet I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13169Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13169Q\"></sup>argue my ways to his face.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This will be my salvation,that the godless shall not come before him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13171R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13171R\"></sup>Keep listening to my words,and let my declaration be in your ears.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Behold, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13172S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13172S\"></sup>prepared my case;I know that I shall be in the right.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13173T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13173T\"></sup>Who is there who will contend with me?For then I would be silent and die.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Only grant me two things,then I will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13174U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13174U\"></sup>hide myself from your face:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13175V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13175V\"></sup>withdraw your hand far from me,and let not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13175W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13175W\"></sup>dread of you terrify me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13176X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13176X\"></sup>Then call, and I will answer;or let me speak, and you reply to me.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>How many are my iniquities and my sins?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13177Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13177Y\"></sup>Make me know my transgression and my sin.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13178Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13178Z\"></sup>do you hide your faceand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13178AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13178AA\"></sup>count me as your enemy?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Will you frighten <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13179AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13179AB\"></sup>a driven leafand pursue dry <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13179AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13179AC\"></sup>chaff?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13180AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13180AD\"></sup>write bitter things against meand make me inherit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13180AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13180AE\"></sup>the iniquities of my youth.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>You put my feet in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13181AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13181AF\"></sup>the stocksand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13181AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13181AG\"></sup>watch all my paths;you set a limit for the soles of my feet.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Man wastes away like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13182AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13182AH\"></sup>a rotten thing,like a garment that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13182AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13182AI\"></sup>moth-eaten."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>“Man who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13183A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13183A\"></sup>born of a womanis <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13183B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13183B\"></sup>few of days and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13183C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13183C\"></sup>full of trouble.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He comes out like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13184D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13184D\"></sup>a flower and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13184E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13184E\"></sup>withers;he flees like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13184F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13184F\"></sup>a shadow and continues not.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13185G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13185G\"></sup>open your eyes on such a oneand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13185H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13185H\"></sup>bring me into judgment with you?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who can bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13186I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13186I\"></sup>a clean thing out of an unclean?There is not one.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Since his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13187J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13187J\"></sup>days are determined,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13187K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13187K\"></sup>the number of his months is with you,and you have appointed his limits that he cannot pass,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13188L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13188L\"></sup>look away from him and leave him alone,that he may enjoy, like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13188M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13188M\"></sup>a hired hand, his day.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“For there is hope for a tree,if it be cut down, that it will sprout again,and that its shoots will not cease.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Though its root grow old in the earth,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13190N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13190N\"></sup>its stump die in the soil,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>yet at the scent of water it will budand put out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13191O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13191O\"></sup>branches like a young plant.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But a man dies and is laid low;man breathes his last, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13192P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13192P\"></sup>where is he?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13193Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13193Q\"></sup>As waters fail from a lakeand a river wastes away and dries up,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>so a man lies down and rises not again;till <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13194R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13194R\"></sup>the heavens are no more he will not awakeor be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13194S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13194S\"></sup>roused out of his sleep.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Oh that you would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13195T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13195T\"></sup>hide me in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13195U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13195U\"></sup>Sheol,that you would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13195V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13195V\"></sup>conceal me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13195W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13195W\"></sup>until your wrath be past,that you would appoint me a set time, and remember me!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If a man dies, shall he live again?All the days of my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13196X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13196X\"></sup>service I would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13196Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13196Y\"></sup>wait,till my renewal should come.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13197Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13197Z\"></sup>call, and I would answer you;you would long for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13197AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13197AA\"></sup>work of your hands.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For then you would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13198AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13198AB\"></sup>number my steps;you would not keep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13198AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13198AC\"></sup>watch over my sin;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>my transgression would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13199AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13199AD\"></sup>sealed up in a bag,and you would cover over my iniquity.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“But the mountain falls and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13200AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13200AE\"></sup>crumbles away,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13200AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13200AF\"></sup>the rock is removed from its place;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>the waters wear away the stones;the torrents wash away the soil of the earth;so you destroy the hope of man.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You prevail forever against him, and he passes;you change his countenance, and send him away.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>His sons come to honor, and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13203AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13203AG\"></sup>does not know it;they are brought low, and he perceives it not.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He feels only the pain of his own body,and he mourns only for himself.”"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13205A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13205A\"></sup>Eliphaz the Temanite answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13206B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13206B\"></sup>a wise man answer with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13206C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13206C\"></sup>windy knowledge,and fill his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13206D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13206D\"></sup>belly with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13206E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13206E\"></sup>the east wind?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Should he argue in unprofitable talk,or in words with which he can do no good?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But you are doing away with the fear of Godand hindering meditation before God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For your iniquity teaches your mouth,and you choose the tongue of the crafty.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13210F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13210F\"></sup>own mouth condemns you, and not I;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13210G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13210G\"></sup>your own lips testify against you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13211H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13211H\"></sup>“Are you the first man who was born?Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13211I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13211I\"></sup>were you brought forth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13211J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13211J\"></sup>before the hills?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Have you listened in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13212K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13212K\"></sup>the council of God?And do you limit wisdom to yourself?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13213L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13213L\"></sup>What do you know that we do not know?What do you understand that is not clear to us?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13214M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13214M\"></sup>Both the gray-haired and the aged are among us,older than your father.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Are the comforts of God too small for you,or the word that deals gently with you?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Why does your heart carry you away,and why do your eyes flash,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>that you turn your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13217N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13217N\"></sup>spirit against Godand bring such words out of your mouth?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13218O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13218O\"></sup>What is man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13218P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13218P\"></sup>that he can be pure?Or he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13218Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13218Q\"></sup>born of a woman, that he can be righteous?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Behold, God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13219R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13219R\"></sup>puts no trust in his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13219S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13219S\"></sup>holy ones,and the heavens are not pure in his sight;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13220T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13220T\"></sup>how much less one who is abominable and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13220U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13220U\"></sup>corrupt,a man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13220V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13220V\"></sup>drinks injustice like water!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“I will show you; hear me,and what I have seen I will declare",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>(what wise men have told,without hiding it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13222W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13222W\"></sup>from their fathers,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>to whom alone the land was given,and no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13223X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13223X\"></sup>stranger passed among them).",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The wicked man writhes in pain all his days,through all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13224Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13224Y\"></sup>years that are laid up for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13224Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13224Z\"></sup>the ruthless.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13225AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13225AA\"></sup>Dreadful sounds are in his ears;in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13225AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13225AB\"></sup>prosperity the destroyer will come upon him.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He does not believe that he will return out of darkness,and he is marked for the sword.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13227AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13227AC\"></sup>wanders abroad for bread, saying, ‘Where is it?’He knows that a day of darkness is ready at his hand;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>distress and anguish terrify him;they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13228AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13228AD\"></sup>prevail against him, like a king ready for battle.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Because he has stretched out his hand against Godand defies the Almighty,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13230AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13230AE\"></sup>running <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13230AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13230AF\"></sup>stubbornly against himwith a thickly bossed shield;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>because he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13231AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13231AG\"></sup>covered his face with his fatand gathered fat upon his waist",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>and has lived in desolate cities,in houses that none should inhabit,which were ready to become heaps of ruins;",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>he will not be rich, and his wealth will not endure,nor will his possessions spread over the earth;",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>he will not depart from darkness;the flame will dry up his shoots,and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13234AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13234AH\"></sup>the breath of his mouth he will depart.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Let him not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13235AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13235AI\"></sup>trust in emptiness, deceiving himself,for emptiness will be his payment.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>It will be paid in full <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13236AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13236AJ\"></sup>before his time,and his branch will not be green.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>He will shake off his unripe grape like the vine,and cast off his blossom like the olive tree.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13238AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13238AK\"></sup>the company of the godless is barren,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13238AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13238AL\"></sup>fire consumes the tents of bribery.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13239AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13239AM\"></sup>conceive trouble and give birth to evil,and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13239AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13239AN\"></sup>womb prepares deceit.”"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Then Job answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I have heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13241A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13241A\"></sup>many such things;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13241B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13241B\"></sup>miserable comforters are you all.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13242C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13242C\"></sup>windy words have an end?Or what provokes you that you answer?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I also could speak as you do,if you were in my place;I could join words together against youand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13243D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13243D\"></sup>shake my head at you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I could strengthen you with my mouth,and the solace of my lips would assuage your pain.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“If I speak, my pain is not assuaged,and if I forbear, how much of it leaves me?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Surely now God has worn me out;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13246E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13246E\"></sup>he has made desolate all my company.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And he has shriveled me up,which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13247F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13247F\"></sup>a witness against me,and my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13247G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13247G\"></sup>leanness has risen up against me;it testifies to my face.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13248H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13248H\"></sup>torn me in his wrath <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13248I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13248I\"></sup>and hated me;he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13248J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13248J\"></sup>gnashed his teeth at me;my adversary sharpens his eyes against me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Men have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13249K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13249K\"></sup>gaped at me with their mouth;they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13249L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13249L\"></sup>struck me insolently on the cheek;they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13249M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13249M\"></sup>mass themselves together against me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>God gives me up to the ungodlyand casts me into the hands of the wicked.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I was at ease, and he broke me apart;he seized me by the neck and dashed me to pieces;he set me up as his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13251N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13251N\"></sup>target;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13252O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13252O\"></sup>archers surround me.He slashes open my kidneys <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13252P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13252P\"></sup>and does not spare;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13252Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13252Q\"></sup>pours out my gall on the ground.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He breaks me with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13253R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13253R\"></sup>breach upon breach;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13253S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13253S\"></sup>runs upon me like a warrior.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I have sewed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13254T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13254T\"></sup>sackcloth upon my skinand have laid <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13254U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13254U\"></sup>my strength <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13254V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13254V\"></sup>in the dust.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>My face is red with weeping,and on my eyelids is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13255W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13255W\"></sup>deep darkness,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>although there is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13256X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13256X\"></sup>violence in my hands,and my prayer is pure.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“O earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13257Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13257Y\"></sup>cover not my blood,and let my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13257Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13257Z\"></sup>cry find no resting place.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Even now, behold, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13258AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13258AA\"></sup>witness is in heaven,and he who testifies for me is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13258AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13258AB\"></sup>on high.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>My friends <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13259AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13259AC\"></sup>scorn me;my eye pours out tears to God,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>that he would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13260AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13260AD\"></sup>argue the case of a man with God,as a son of man does with his neighbor.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For when a few years have comeI shall go the way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13261AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13261AE\"></sup>from which I shall not return."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>“My spirit is broken; my days are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13262A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13262A\"></sup>extinct;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13262B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13262B\"></sup>the graveyard is ready for me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Surely there are mockers about me,and my eye dwells on their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13263C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13263C\"></sup>provocation.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Lay down a pledge for me with you;who is there who will put up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13264D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13264D\"></sup>security for me?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Since you have closed their hearts to understanding,therefore you will not let them triumph.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He who informs against his friends to get a share of their property—the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13266E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13266E\"></sup>eyes of his children will fail.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“He has made me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13267F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13267F\"></sup>a byword of the peoples,and I am one before whom men spit.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13268G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13268G\"></sup>eye has grown dim from vexation,and all my members are like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13268H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13268H\"></sup>a shadow.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The upright are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13269I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13269I\"></sup>appalled at this,and the innocent stirs himself up against the godless.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Yet the righteous holds to his way,and he who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13270J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13270J\"></sup>clean hands grows stronger and stronger.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13271K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13271K\"></sup>come on again, all of you,and I shall not find a wise man among you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13272L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13272L\"></sup>days are past; my plans are broken off,the desires of my heart.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13273M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13273M\"></sup>make night into day:‘The light,’ they say, ‘is near to the darkness.’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If I hope for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13274N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13274N\"></sup>Sheol as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13274O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13274O\"></sup>my house,if I make my bed in darkness,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>if I say to the pit, ‘You are my father,’and to the worm, ‘My mother,’ or ‘My sister,’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>where then is my hope?Who will see my hope?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Will it go down to the bars of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13277P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13277P\"></sup>Sheol?Shall we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13277Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13277Q\"></sup>descend together <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13277R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13277R\"></sup>into the dust?”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13278A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13278A\"></sup>Bildad the Shuhite answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How long will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13279B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13279B\"></sup>hunt for words?Consider, and then we will speak.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Why are we counted as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13280C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13280C\"></sup>cattle?Why are we stupid in your sight?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13281D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13281D\"></sup>tear yourself in your anger,shall the earth be forsaken for you,or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13281E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13281E\"></sup>the rock be removed out of its place?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Indeed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13282F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13282F\"></sup>the light of the wicked is put out,and the flame of his fire does not shine.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The light is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13283G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13283G\"></sup>dark in his tent,and his lamp above him is put out.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>His strong steps are shortened,and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13284H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13284H\"></sup>own schemes throw him down.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For he is cast into a net by his own feet,and he walks on its mesh.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13286I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13286I\"></sup>A trap seizes him by the heel;a snare lays hold of him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>A rope is hidden for him in the ground,a trap for him in the path.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13288J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13288J\"></sup>Terrors frighten him on every side,and chase him at his heels.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>His strength is famished,and calamity is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13289K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13289K\"></sup>ready for his stumbling.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>It consumes the parts of his skin;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13290L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13290L\"></sup>the firstborn of death consumes his limbs.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He is torn from the tent in which he trustedand is brought to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13291M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13291M\"></sup>the king of terrors.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In his tent dwells that which is none of his;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13292N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13292N\"></sup>sulfur is scattered over his habitation.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13293O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13293O\"></sup>roots dry up beneath,and his branches <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13293P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13293P\"></sup>wither above.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13294Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13294Q\"></sup>memory perishes from the earth,and he has no name in the street.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13295R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13295R\"></sup>He is thrust from light into darkness,and driven out of the world.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He has no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13296S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13296S\"></sup>posterity or progeny among his people,and no survivor where he used to live.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They of the west are appalled at his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13297T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13297T\"></sup>day,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13297U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13297U\"></sup>horror seizes them of the east.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Surely such are the dwellings of the unrighteous,such is the place of him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13298V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13298V\"></sup>knows not God.”"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>Then Job answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How long will you torment meand break me in pieces with words?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>These <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13301A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13301A\"></sup>ten times you have cast reproach upon me;are you not ashamed to wrong me?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And even if it be true that I have erred,my error remains with myself.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If indeed you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13303B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13303B\"></sup>magnify yourselves against meand make my disgrace an argument against me,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>know then that God has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13304C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13304C\"></sup>put me in the wrongand closed his net about me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Behold, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13305D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13305D\"></sup>cry out, ‘Violence!’ but I am not answered;I call for help, but there is no justice.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13306E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13306E\"></sup>walled up my way, so that I cannot pass,and he has set darkness upon my paths.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13307F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13307F\"></sup>stripped from me my gloryand taken the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13307G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13307G\"></sup>crown from my head.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He breaks me down on every side, and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13308H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13308H\"></sup>am gone,and my hope has he pulled up like a tree.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He has kindled his wrath against meand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13309I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13309I\"></sup>counts me as his adversary.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13310J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13310J\"></sup>troops come on together;they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13310K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13310K\"></sup>cast up their siege ramp against meand encamp around my tent.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“He has put my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13311L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13311L\"></sup>brothers far from me,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13311M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13311M\"></sup>those who knew me are wholly estranged from me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>My relatives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13312N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13312N\"></sup>have failed me,my close <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13312O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13312O\"></sup>friends have forgotten me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The guests <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13313P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13313P\"></sup>in my house and my maidservants count me as a stranger;I have become a foreigner in their eyes.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I call to my servant, but he gives me no answer;I must plead with him with my mouth for mercy.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>My breath is strange to my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13315Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13315Q\"></sup>wife,and I am a stench to the children of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13315R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13315R\"></sup>my own mother.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Even young <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13316S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13316S\"></sup>children despise me;when I rise they talk against me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>All my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13317T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13317T\"></sup>intimate friends abhor me,and those whom I loved have turned against me.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13318U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13318U\"></sup>bones stick to my skin and to my flesh,and I have escaped by the skin of my teeth.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Have mercy on me, have mercy on me, O you my friends,for the hand of God has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13319V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13319V\"></sup>touched me!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Why do you, like God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13320W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13320W\"></sup>pursue me?Why are you not satisfied with my flesh?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Oh that my words were written!Oh that they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13321X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13321X\"></sup>inscribed in a book!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Oh that with an iron <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13322Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13322Y\"></sup>pen and leadthey were engraved in the rock forever!",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13323Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13323Z\"></sup>know that my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13323AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13323AA\"></sup>Redeemer lives,and at the last he will stand upon the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13323AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13323AB\"></sup>earth.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And after my skin has been thus destroyed,yet in my flesh I shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13324AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13324AC\"></sup>see God,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>whom I shall see for myself,and my eyes shall behold, and not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13325AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13325AD\"></sup>another.My heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13325AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13325AE\"></sup>faints within me!",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>If you say, ‘How we will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13326AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13326AF\"></sup>pursue him!’and, ‘The root of the matter is found in him,’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>be afraid of the sword,for wrath brings the punishment of the sword,that you may know there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13327AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13327AG\"></sup>a judgment.”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13328A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13328A\"></sup>Zophar the Naamathite answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Therefore my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13329B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13329B\"></sup>thoughts answer me,because of my haste within me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I hear censure that insults me,and out of my understanding a spirit answers me.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Do you not know this from of old,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13331C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13331C\"></sup>since man was placed on earth,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13332D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13332D\"></sup>that the exulting of the wicked is short,and the joy of the godless but for a moment?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13333E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13333E\"></sup>Though his height mount up to the heavens,and his head reach to the clouds,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>he will perish forever like his own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13334F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13334F\"></sup>dung;those who have seen him will say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13334G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13334G\"></sup>‘Where is he?’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He will fly away like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13335H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13335H\"></sup>a dream and not be found;he will be chased away like a vision of the night.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13336I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13336I\"></sup>The eye that saw him will see him no more,nor will his place any more behold him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>His children will seek the favor of the poor,and his hands will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13337J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13337J\"></sup>give back his wealth.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>His bones are full of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13338K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13338K\"></sup>youthful vigor,but it will lie <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13338L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13338L\"></sup>down with him in the dust.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Though evil is sweet in his mouth,though he hides it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13339M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13339M\"></sup>under his tongue,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>though he is loath to let it goand holds it in his mouth,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>yet his food is turned in his stomach;it is the venom of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13341N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13341N\"></sup>cobras within him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He swallows down riches and vomits them up again;God casts them out of his belly.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He will suck the poison of cobras;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13343O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13343O\"></sup>the tongue of a viper will kill him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He will not look upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13344P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13344P\"></sup>the rivers,the streams flowing with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13344Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13344Q\"></sup>honey and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13344R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13344R\"></sup>curds.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13345S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13345S\"></sup>give back the fruit of his toiland will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13345T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13345T\"></sup>swallow it down;from the profit of his tradinghe will get no enjoyment.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For he has crushed and abandoned the poor;he has seized a house that he did not build.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Because he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13347U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13347U\"></sup>knew no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13347V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13347V\"></sup>contentment in his belly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13347W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13347W\"></sup>he will not let anything in which he delights escape him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>There was nothing left after he had eaten;therefore his prosperity will not endure.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>In the fullness of his sufficiency he will be in distress;the hand of everyone in misery will come against him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>To fill his belly to the full,God will send his burning anger against himand rain it upon him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13350X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13350X\"></sup>into his body.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13351Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13351Y\"></sup>He will flee from an iron weapon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13351Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13351Z\"></sup>a bronze arrow will strike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13351AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13351AA\"></sup>him through.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>It <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13352AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13352AB\"></sup>is drawn forth and comes out of his body;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13352AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13352AC\"></sup>the glittering point comes out of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13352AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13352AD\"></sup>gallbladder;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13352AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13352AE\"></sup>terrors come upon him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Utter darkness is laid up for his treasures;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13353AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13353AF\"></sup>a fire not fanned will devour him;what is left in his tent will be consumed.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13354AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13354AG\"></sup>The heavens will reveal his iniquity,and the earth will rise up against him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The possessions of his house will be carried away,dragged off in the day of God's wrath.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13356AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13356AH\"></sup>This is the wicked man's portion from God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13356AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13356AI\"></sup>the heritage decreed for him by God.”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>Then Job answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13358A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13358A\"></sup>“Keep listening to my words,and let this be your comfort.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Bear with me, and I will speak,and after I have spoken, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13359B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13359B\"></sup>mock on.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>As for me, is my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13360C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13360C\"></sup>complaint against man?Why should I not be impatient?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Look at me and be appalled,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13361D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13361D\"></sup>lay your hand over your mouth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When I remember, I am dismayed,and shuddering seizes my flesh.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13363E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13363E\"></sup>Why do the wicked live,reach old age, and grow mighty in power?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13364F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13364F\"></sup>offspring are established in their presence,and their descendants before their eyes.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Their houses are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13365G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13365G\"></sup>safe from fear,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13365H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13365H\"></sup>no rod of God is upon them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Their bull breeds without fail;their cow calves and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13366I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13366I\"></sup>does not miscarry.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They send out their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13367J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13367J\"></sup>little boys like a flock,and their children dance.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They sing to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13368K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13368K\"></sup>the tambourine and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13368L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13368L\"></sup>the lyreand rejoice to the sound of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13368M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13368M\"></sup>the pipe.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13369N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13369N\"></sup>spend their days in prosperity,and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13369O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13369O\"></sup>peace they go down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13369P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13369P\"></sup>Sheol.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They say to God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13370Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13370Q\"></sup>‘Depart from us!We do not desire the knowledge of your ways.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13371R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13371R\"></sup>What is the Almighty, that we should serve him?And what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13371S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13371S\"></sup>profit do we get if we pray to him?’",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Behold, is not their prosperity in their hand?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13372T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13372T\"></sup>The counsel of the wicked is far from me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“How often is it that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13373U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13373U\"></sup>the lamp of the wicked is put out?That their calamity comes upon them?That God distributes pains in his anger?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>That they are like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13374V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13374V\"></sup>straw before the wind,and like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13374W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13374W\"></sup>chaff that the storm carries away?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You say, ‘God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13375X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13375X\"></sup>stores up their iniquity for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13375Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13375Y\"></sup>children.’Let him pay it out to them, that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13375Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13375Z\"></sup>know it.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Let their own eyes see their destruction,and let them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13376AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13376AA\"></sup>drink of the wrath of the Almighty.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For what do they care for their houses after them,when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13377AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13377AB\"></sup>the number of their months is cut off?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13378AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13378AC\"></sup>Will any teach God knowledge,seeing that he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13378AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13378AD\"></sup>judges those who are on high?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>One dies in his full vigor,being wholly at ease and secure,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>his pails full of milkand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13380AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13380AE\"></sup>the marrow of his bones moist.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Another dies in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13381AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13381AF\"></sup>bitterness of soul,never having tasted of prosperity.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13382AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13382AG\"></sup>lie down alike in the dust,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13382AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13382AH\"></sup>the worms cover them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Behold, I know your thoughtsand your schemes to wrong me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For you say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13384AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13384AI\"></sup>‘Where is the house of the prince?Where is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13384AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13384AJ\"></sup>the tent in which the wicked lived?’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Have you not asked those who travel the roads,and do you not accept their testimony",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13386AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13386AK\"></sup>the evil man is spared in the day of calamity,that he is rescued in the day of wrath?",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Who declares his way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13387AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13387AL\"></sup>to his face,and who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13387AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13387AM\"></sup>repays him for what he has done?",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>When he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13388AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13388AN\"></sup>carried to the grave,watch is kept over his tomb.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13389AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13389AO\"></sup>The clods of the valley are sweet to him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13389AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13389AP\"></sup>all mankind follows after him,and those who go before him are innumerable.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>How then will you comfort me with empty nothings?There is nothing left of your answers but falsehood.”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13391A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13391A\"></sup>Eliphaz the Temanite answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13392B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13392B\"></sup>“Can a man be profitable to God?Surely he who is wise is profitable to himself.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Is it any pleasure to the Almighty if you are in the right,or is it gain to him if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13393C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13393C\"></sup>make your ways blameless?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Is it for your fear of him that he reproves youand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13394D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13394D\"></sup>enters into judgment with you?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Is not your evil abundant?There is no end to your iniquities.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13396E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13396E\"></sup>exacted pledges of your brothers for nothing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13396F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13396F\"></sup>and stripped the naked of their clothing.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You have given no water to the weary to drink,and you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13397G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13397G\"></sup>withheld bread from the hungry.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13398H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13398H\"></sup>The man with power possessed the land,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13398I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13398I\"></sup>the favored man lived in it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13399J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13399J\"></sup>sent widows away empty,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13399K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13399K\"></sup>the arms of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13399L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13399L\"></sup>the fatherless were crushed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13400M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13400M\"></sup>snares are all around you,and sudden terror overwhelms you,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13401N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13401N\"></sup>darkness, so that you cannot see,and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13401O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13401O\"></sup>flood of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13401P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13401P\"></sup>water covers you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Is not God high in the heavens?See <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13402Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13402Q\"></sup>the highest stars, how lofty they are!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But you say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13403R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13403R\"></sup>‘What does God know?Can he judge through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13403S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13403S\"></sup>the deep darkness?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13404T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13404T\"></sup>Thick clouds veil him, so that he does not see,and he walks on the vault of heaven.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Will you keep to the old waythat wicked men have trod?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They were snatched away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13406U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13406U\"></sup>before their time;their foundation was washed away.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They said to God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13407V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13407V\"></sup>‘Depart from us,’and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13407W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13407W\"></sup>‘What can the Almighty do to us?’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Yet he filled their houses with good things—but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13408X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13408X\"></sup>the counsel of the wicked is far from me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13409Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13409Y\"></sup>The righteous see it and are glad;the innocent one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13409Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13409Z\"></sup>mocks at them,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>saying, ‘Surely our adversaries are cut off,and what they left <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13410AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13410AA\"></sup>the fire has consumed.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13411AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13411AB\"></sup>“Agree with God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13411AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13411AC\"></sup>be at peace;thereby good will come to you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Receive instruction from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13412AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13412AD\"></sup>his mouth,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13412AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13412AE\"></sup>lay up his words in your heart.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>If you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13413AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13413AF\"></sup>return to the Almighty you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13413AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13413AG\"></sup>built up;if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13413AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13413AH\"></sup>remove injustice far from your tents,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>if you lay gold in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13414AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13414AI\"></sup>the dust,and gold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13414AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13414AJ\"></sup>Ophir among the stones of the torrent-bed,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>then the Almighty will be your goldand your precious silver.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For then you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13416AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13416AK\"></sup>will delight yourself in the Almightyand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13416AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13416AL\"></sup>lift up your face to God.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13417AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13417AM\"></sup>make your prayer to him, and he will hear you,and you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13417AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13417AN\"></sup>pay your vows.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>You will decide on a matter, and it will be established for you,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13418AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13418AO\"></sup>light will shine on your ways.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For when they are humbled you say, ‘It is because of pride’;but he saves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13419AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13419AP\"></sup>the lowly.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13420AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13420AQ\"></sup>delivers even the one who is not innocent,who will be delivered through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13420AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13420AR\"></sup>the cleanness of your hands.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>Then Job answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Today also my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13422A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13422A\"></sup>complaint is bitter;my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13422B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13422B\"></sup>hand is heavy on account of my groaning.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Oh, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13423C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13423C\"></sup>that I knew where I might find him,that I might come even to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13423D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13423D\"></sup>seat!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13424E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13424E\"></sup>lay my case before himand fill my mouth with arguments.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I would know what he would answer meand understand what he would say to me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Would he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13426F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13426F\"></sup>contend with me in the greatness of his power?No; he would pay attention to me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There an upright man could argue with him,and I would be acquitted forever by my judge.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13428G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13428G\"></sup>I go forward, but he is not there,and backward, but I do not perceive him;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>on the left hand when he is working, I do not behold him;he turns to the right hand, but I do not see him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13430H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13430H\"></sup>knows <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13430I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13430I\"></sup>the way that I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13430J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13430J\"></sup>take;when he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13430K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13430K\"></sup>tried me, I shall come out as gold.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>My foot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13431L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13431L\"></sup>has held fast to his steps;I have kept his way and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13431M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13431M\"></sup>not turned aside.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I have not departed from the commandment of his lips;I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13432N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13432N\"></sup>treasured the words of his mouth more than my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13432O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13432O\"></sup>portion of food.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But he is unchangeable, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13433P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13433P\"></sup>who can turn him back?What he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13433Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13433Q\"></sup>desires, that he does.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For he will complete what he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13434R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13434R\"></sup>appoints for me,and many such things are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13434S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13434S\"></sup>in his mind.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore I am terrified at his presence;when I consider, I am in dread of him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>God has made my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13436T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13436T\"></sup>heart faint;the Almighty has terrified me;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>yet I am not silenced because of the darkness,nor because thick darkness covers my face."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>“Why are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13438A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13438A\"></sup>not times of judgment <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13438B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13438B\"></sup>kept by the Almighty,and why do those who know him never see his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13438C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13438C\"></sup>days?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Some move <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13439D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13439D\"></sup>landmarks;they seize flocks and pasture them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They drive away the donkey of the fatherless;they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13440E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13440E\"></sup>take the widow's ox for a pledge.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13441F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13441F\"></sup>thrust the poor off the road;the poor of the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13441G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13441G\"></sup>all hide themselves.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Behold, like wild donkeys in the desertthe poor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13442H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13442H\"></sup>go out to their toil, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13442I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13442I\"></sup>seeking game;the wasteland yields food for their children.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They gather their fodder in the field,and they glean the vineyard of the wicked man.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13444J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13444J\"></sup>lie all night naked, without clothing,and have no covering in the cold.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They are wet with the rain of the mountainsand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13445K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13445K\"></sup>cling to the rock for lack of shelter.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>(There are those who snatch the fatherless child from the breast,and they take a pledge against the poor.)",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They go about naked, without clothing;hungry, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13447L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13447L\"></sup>carry the sheaves;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>among the olive rows of the wicked they make oil;they tread the winepresses, but suffer thirst.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>From out of the city the dying groan,and the soul of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13449M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13449M\"></sup>the wounded cries for help;yet God charges no one with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13449N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13449N\"></sup>wrong.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“There are those who rebel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13450O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13450O\"></sup>against the light,who are not acquainted with its ways,and do not stay in its paths.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The murderer rises before it is light,that he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13451P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13451P\"></sup>may kill the poor and needy,and in the night he is like a thief.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The eye of the adulterer also waits for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13452Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13452Q\"></sup>the twilight,saying, ‘No <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13452R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13452R\"></sup>eye will see me’;and he veils his face.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In the dark they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13453S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13453S\"></sup>dig through houses;by day they shut themselves up;they do not know the light.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13454T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13454T\"></sup>deep darkness is morning to all of them;for they are friends with the terrors of deep darkness.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“You say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13455U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13455U\"></sup>‘Swift are they on the face of the waters;their portion is cursed in the land;no treader turns toward their vineyards.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Drought and heat snatch away the snow waters;so does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13456V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13456V\"></sup>Sheol those who have sinned.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The womb forgets them;the worm finds them sweet;they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13457W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13457W\"></sup>no longer remembered,so wickedness is broken like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13457X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13457X\"></sup>a tree.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“They wrong the barren, childless woman,and do no good to the widow.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Yet God prolongs the life of the mighty by his power;they rise up when they despair of life.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He gives them security, and they are supported,and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13460Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13460Y\"></sup>eyes are upon their ways.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>They are exalted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13461Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13461Z\"></sup>a little while, and then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13461AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13461AA\"></sup>are gone;they are brought low and gathered up like all others;they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13461AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13461AB\"></sup>cut off like the heads of grain.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>If it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13462AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13462AC\"></sup>not so, who will prove me a liarand show that there is nothing in what I say?”"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13463A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13463A\"></sup>Bildad the Shuhite answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Dominion and fear are with God;he makes peace in his high heaven.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Is there any number to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13465B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13465B\"></sup>armies?Upon whom does his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13465C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13465C\"></sup>light not arise?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>How then can man be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13466D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13466D\"></sup>in the right before God?How can he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13466E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13466E\"></sup>born of woman be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13466F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13466F\"></sup>pure?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Behold, even the moon is not bright,and the stars are not pure in his eyes;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13468G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13468G\"></sup>how much less man, who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13468H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13468H\"></sup>a maggot,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13468I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13468I\"></sup>the son of man, who is a worm!”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>Then Job answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13470A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13470A\"></sup>helped him who has no power!How you have saved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13470B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13470B\"></sup>the arm that has no strength!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>How you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13471C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13471C\"></sup>counseled him who has no wisdom,and plentifully declared sound knowledge!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>With whose help have you uttered words,and whose breath <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13472D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13472D\"></sup>has come out from you?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13473E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13473E\"></sup>dead trembleunder the waters and their inhabitants.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Sheol is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13474F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13474F\"></sup>naked before God,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13474G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13474G\"></sup>Abaddon has no covering.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13475H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13475H\"></sup>stretches out the north over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13475I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13475I\"></sup>the voidand hangs the earth on nothing.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13476J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13476J\"></sup>binds up the waters in his thick clouds,and the cloud is not split open under them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He covers the face of the full moonand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13477K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13477K\"></sup>spreads over it his cloud.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He has inscribed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13478L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13478L\"></sup>a circle on the face of the watersat the boundary between light and darkness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13479M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13479M\"></sup>The pillars of heaven trembleand are astounded at his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13479N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13479N\"></sup>rebuke.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>By his power he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13480O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13480O\"></sup>stilled the sea;by his understanding he shattered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13480P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13480P\"></sup>Rahab.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13481Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13481Q\"></sup>By his wind the heavens were made fair;his hand pierced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13481R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13481R\"></sup>the fleeing serpent.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Behold, these are but the outskirts of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13482S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13482S\"></sup>ways,and how small <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13482T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13482T\"></sup>a whisper do we hear of him!But the thunder of his power who can understand?”"
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>And Job again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13483A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13483A\"></sup>took up his discourse, and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“As God lives, who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13484B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13484B\"></sup>taken away my right,and the Almighty, who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13484C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13484C\"></sup>made my soul bitter,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>as long as my breath is in me,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13485D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13485D\"></sup>the spirit of God is in my nostrils,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>my lips will not speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13486E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13486E\"></sup>falsehood,and my tongue will not utter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13486F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13486F\"></sup>deceit.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Far be it from me to say that you are right;till I die I will not put away my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13487G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13487G\"></sup>integrity from me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13488H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13488H\"></sup>hold fast my righteousness and will not let it go;my heart does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13488I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13488I\"></sup>reproach me for any of my days.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Let my enemy be as the wicked,and let him who rises up against me be as the unrighteous.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13490J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13490J\"></sup>For what is the hope of the godless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13490K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13490K\"></sup>when God cuts him off,when God takes away his life?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13491L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13491L\"></sup>Will God hear his crywhen distress comes upon him?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Will he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13492M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13492M\"></sup>take delight in the Almighty?Will he call upon God at all times?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I will teach you concerning the hand of God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13493N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13493N\"></sup>what is with the Almighty I will not conceal.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Behold, all of you have seen it yourselves;why then have you become altogether vain?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13495O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13495O\"></sup>“This is the portion of a wicked man with God,and the heritage that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13495P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13495P\"></sup>oppressors receive from the Almighty:",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13496Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13496Q\"></sup>children are multiplied, it is for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13496R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13496R\"></sup>the sword,and his descendants have not enough bread.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Those who survive him the pestilence buries,and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13497S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13497S\"></sup>widows do not weep.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Though he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13498T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13498T\"></sup>heap up silver like dust,and pile up clothing like clay,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>he may pile it up, but the righteous will wear it,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13499U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13499U\"></sup>the innocent will divide the silver.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He builds his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13500V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13500V\"></sup>house like a moth's,like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13500W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13500W\"></sup>a booth that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13500X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13500X\"></sup>a watchman makes.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He goes to bed rich, but will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13501Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13501Y\"></sup>do so no more;he opens his eyes, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13501Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13501Z\"></sup>his wealth is gone.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13502AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13502AA\"></sup>Terrors overtake him like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13502AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13502AB\"></sup>a flood;in the night a whirlwind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13502AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13502AC\"></sup>carries him off.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13503AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13503AD\"></sup>The east wind lifts him up and he is gone;it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13503AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13503AE\"></sup>sweeps him out of his place.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>It hurls at him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13504AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13504AF\"></sup>without pity;he flees from its power in headlong flight.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>It <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13505AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13505AG\"></sup>claps its hands at himand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13505AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13505AH\"></sup>hisses at him from its place."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>“Surely there is a mine for silver,and a place for gold that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13506A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13506A\"></sup>refine.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Iron is taken out of the earth,and copper is smelted from the ore.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Man puts an end to darknessand searches out to the farthest limitthe ore in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13508B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13508B\"></sup>gloom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13508C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13508C\"></sup>deep darkness.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He opens shafts in a valley away from where anyone lives;they are forgotten by travelers;they hang in the air, far away from mankind; they swing to and fro.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>As for the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13510D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13510D\"></sup>out of it comes bread,but underneath it is turned up as by fire.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Its stones are the place of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13511E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13511E\"></sup>sapphires,and it has dust of gold.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“That path no bird of prey knows,and the falcon's eye has not seen it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13513F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13513F\"></sup>The proud beasts have not trodden it;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13513G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13513G\"></sup>the lion has not passed over it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Man puts his hand to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13514H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13514H\"></sup>the flinty rockand overturns mountains by the roots.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He cuts out channels in the rocks,and his eye sees every precious thing.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He dams up the streams so that they do not trickle,and the thing that is hidden he brings out to light.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13517I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13517I\"></sup>“But where shall wisdom be found?And where is the place of understanding?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Man does not know its worth,and it is not found in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13518J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13518J\"></sup>the land of the living.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13519K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13519K\"></sup>The deep says, ‘It is not in me,’and the sea says, ‘It is not with me.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>It <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13520L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13520L\"></sup>cannot be bought for gold,and silver cannot be weighed as its price.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>It cannot be valued in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13521M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13521M\"></sup>the gold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13521N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13521N\"></sup>Ophir,in precious <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13521O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13521O\"></sup>onyx or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13521P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13521P\"></sup>sapphire.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Gold and glass cannot equal it,nor can it be exchanged for jewels of fine gold.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>No mention shall be made of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13523Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13523Q\"></sup>coral or of crystal;the price of wisdom is above <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13523R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13523R\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13523S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13523S\"></sup>pearls.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13524T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13524T\"></sup>The topaz of Ethiopia cannot equal it,nor can it be valued in pure gold.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“From where, then, does wisdom come?And where is the place of understanding?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>It is hidden from the eyes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13526U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13526U\"></sup>all livingand concealed from the birds of the air.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13527V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13527V\"></sup>Abaddon and Death say,‘We have heard a rumor of it with our ears.’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13528W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13528W\"></sup>“God understands the way to it,and he knows its place.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13529X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13529X\"></sup>looks to the ends of the earthand sees everything under the heavens.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13530Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13530Y\"></sup>gave to the wind its weightand apportioned the waters by measure,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>when he made a decree for the rainand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13531Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13531Z\"></sup>a way for the lightning of the thunder,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>then he saw it and declared it;he established it, and searched it out.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And he said to man,‘Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13533AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13533AA\"></sup>the fear of the Lord, that is wisdom,and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13533AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13533AB\"></sup>turn away from evil is understanding.’”"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>And Job again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13534A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13534A\"></sup>took up his discourse, and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Oh, that I were as in the months of old,as in the days when God watched over me,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>when his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13536B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13536B\"></sup>lamp shone upon my head,and by his light I walked through darkness,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>as I was in my prime,when the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13537C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13537C\"></sup>friendship of God was upon my tent,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>when the Almighty was yet with me,when my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13538D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13538D\"></sup>children were all around me,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>when my steps were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13539E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13539E\"></sup>washed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13539F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13539F\"></sup>butter,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13539G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13539G\"></sup>the rock poured out for me streams of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13539H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13539H\"></sup>oil!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When I went out to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13540I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13540I\"></sup>the gate of the city,when I prepared my seat in the square,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>the young men saw me and withdrew,and the aged rose and stood;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>the princes refrained from talkingand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13542J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13542J\"></sup>laid their hand on their mouth;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>the voice of the nobles was hushed,and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13543K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13543K\"></sup>tongue stuck to the roof of their mouth.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When the ear heard, it called me blessed,and when the eye saw, it approved,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>because I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13545L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13545L\"></sup>delivered the poor who cried for help,and the fatherless who had none to help him.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13546M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13546M\"></sup>The blessing of him who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13546N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13546N\"></sup>about to perish came upon me,and I caused <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13546O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13546O\"></sup>the widow's heart to sing for joy.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13547P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13547P\"></sup>put on righteousness, and it clothed me;my justice was like a robe and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13547Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13547Q\"></sup>a turban.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13548R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13548R\"></sup>eyes to the blindand feet to the lame.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I was a father to the needy,and I searched out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13549S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13549S\"></sup>the cause of him whom I did not know.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13550T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13550T\"></sup>broke <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13550U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13550U\"></sup>the fangs of the unrighteousand made him drop his prey from his teeth.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13551V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13551V\"></sup>Then I thought, ‘I shall die in my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13551W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13551W\"></sup>nest,and I shall multiply my days as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13551X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13551X\"></sup>the sand,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13552Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13552Y\"></sup>roots spread out to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13552Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13552Z\"></sup>the waters,with the dew all night on my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13552AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13552AA\"></sup>branches,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>my glory fresh with me,and my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13553AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13553AB\"></sup>bow ever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13553AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13553AC\"></sup>new in my hand.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Men listened to me and waitedand kept silence for my counsel.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>After I spoke they did not speak again,and my word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13555AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13555AD\"></sup>dropped upon them.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They waited for me as for the rain,and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13556AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13556AE\"></sup>opened their mouths as for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13556AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13556AF\"></sup>spring rain.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I smiled on them when they had no confidence,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13557AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13557AG\"></sup>the light of my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13557AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13557AH\"></sup>face they did not cast down.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I chose their way and sat as chief,and I lived like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13558AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13558AI\"></sup>a king among his troops,like one who comforts mourners."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>“But now they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13559A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13559A\"></sup>laugh at me,men who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13559B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13559B\"></sup>younger than I,whose fathers I would have disdainedto set with the dogs of my flock.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>What could I gain from the strength of their hands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13560C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13560C\"></sup>men whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13560D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13560D\"></sup>vigor is gone?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Through want and hard hungerthey <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13561E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13561E\"></sup>gnaw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13561F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13561F\"></sup>the dry ground by night in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13561G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13561G\"></sup>waste and desolation;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>they pick saltwort and the leaves of bushes,and the roots of the broom tree for their food.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13563H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13563H\"></sup>They are driven out from human company;they shout after them as after a thief.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In the gullies of the torrents they must dwell,in holes of the earth and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13564I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13564I\"></sup>the rocks.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Among the bushes they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13565J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13565J\"></sup>bray;under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13565K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13565K\"></sup>the nettles they huddle together.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>A senseless, a nameless brood,they have been whipped out of the land.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“And now I have become their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13567L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13567L\"></sup>song;I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13567M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13567M\"></sup>a byword to them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13568N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13568N\"></sup>abhor me; they keep aloof from me;they do not hesitate to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13568O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13568O\"></sup>spit at the sight of me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Because God has loosed my cord and humbled me,they have cast off restraint in my presence.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>On my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13570P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13570P\"></sup>right hand the rabble rise;they push away my feet;they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13570Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13570Q\"></sup>cast up against me their ways of destruction.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They break up my path;they promote my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13571R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13571R\"></sup>calamity;they need no one to help them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As through a wide <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13572S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13572S\"></sup>breach they come;amid the crash they roll on.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13573T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13573T\"></sup>Terrors are turned upon me;my honor is pursued as by the wind,and my prosperity has passed away like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13573U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13573U\"></sup>a cloud.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“And now my soul is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13574V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13574V\"></sup>poured out within me;days of affliction have taken hold of me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13575W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13575W\"></sup>The night <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13575X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13575X\"></sup>racks my bones,and the pain that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13575Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13575Y\"></sup>gnaws me takes no rest.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>With great force my garment is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13576Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13576Z\"></sup>disfigured;it binds me about like the collar of my tunic.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>God has cast me into the mire,and I have become like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13577AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13577AA\"></sup>dust and ashes.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I cry to you for help and you do not answer me;I stand, and you only look at me.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13579AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13579AB\"></sup>turned cruel to me;with the might of your hand you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13579AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13579AC\"></sup>persecute me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13580AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13580AD\"></sup>You lift me up on the wind; you make me ride on it,and you toss me about in the roar of the storm.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13581AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13581AE\"></sup>For I know that you will bring me to deathand to the house appointed for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13581AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13581AF\"></sup>all living.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Yet does not one in a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13582AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13582AG\"></sup>heap of ruins stretch out his hand,and in his disaster cry for help?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Did not I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13583AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13583AH\"></sup>weep for him whose day was hard?Was not my soul grieved for the needy?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13584AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13584AI\"></sup>when I hoped for good, evil came,and when I waited for light, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13584AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13584AJ\"></sup>darkness came.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>My inward parts are in turmoil and never still;days of affliction <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13585AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13585AK\"></sup>come to meet me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13586AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13586AL\"></sup>go about darkened, but not by the sun;I stand up in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13586AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13586AM\"></sup>the assembly and cry for help.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I am a brother of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13587AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13587AN\"></sup>jackalsand a companion of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13587AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13587AO\"></sup>ostriches.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13588AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13588AP\"></sup>skin turns black and falls from me,and my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13588AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13588AQ\"></sup>bones burn with heat.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13589AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13589AR\"></sup>lyre is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13589AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13589AS\"></sup>turned to mourning,and my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13589AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13589AT\"></sup>pipe to the voice of those who weep."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>“I have made a covenant with my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13590A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13590A\"></sup>eyes;how then could I gaze at a virgin?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>What would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13591B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13591B\"></sup>my portion from God aboveand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13591C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13591C\"></sup>my heritage from the Almighty on high?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Is not calamity for the unrighteous,and disaster for the workers of iniquity?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13593D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13593D\"></sup>Does not he see my waysand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13593E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13593E\"></sup>number all my steps?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“If I have walked with falsehoodand my foot has hastened to deceit;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>(Let me be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13595F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13595F\"></sup>weighed in a just balance,and let God know my integrity!)",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>if my step has turned aside from the wayand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13596G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13596G\"></sup>my heart has gone after my eyes,and if any <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13596H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13596H\"></sup>spot has stuck to my hands,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>then let me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13597I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13597I\"></sup>sow, and another eat,and let what grows for me be rooted out.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“If my heart has been enticed toward a woman,and I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13598J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13598J\"></sup>lain in wait at my neighbor's door,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>then let my wife <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13599K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13599K\"></sup>grind for another,and let others <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13599L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13599L\"></sup>bow down on her.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For that would be a heinous crime;that would be an iniquity <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13600M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13600M\"></sup>to be punished by the judges;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>for that would be a fire <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13601N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13601N\"></sup>that consumes as far as Abaddon,and it would burn to the root all my increase.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“If I have rejected the cause of my manservant or my maidservant,when they brought a complaint against me,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>what then shall I do when God rises up?When he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13603O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13603O\"></sup>makes inquiry, what shall I answer him?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13604P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13604P\"></sup>not he who made me in the womb make him?And did not one fashion us in the womb?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“If I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13605Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13605Q\"></sup>withheld anything that the poor desired,or have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13605R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13605R\"></sup>caused the eyes of the widow to fail,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>or have eaten my morsel alone,and the fatherless has not eaten of it",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>(for from my youth the fatherless grew up with me as with a father,and from my mother's womb I guided the widow),",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>if I have seen anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13608S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13608S\"></sup>perish for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13608T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13608T\"></sup>lack of clothing,or the needy without <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13608U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13608U\"></sup>covering,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>if his body has not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13609V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13609V\"></sup>blessed me,and if he was not warmed with the fleece of my sheep,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>if I have raised my hand against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13610W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13610W\"></sup>the fatherless,because I saw my help in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13610X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13610X\"></sup>the gate,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>then let my shoulder blade fall from my shoulder,and let my arm be broken from its socket.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13612Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13612Y\"></sup>in terror of calamity from God,and I could not have faced his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13612Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13612Z\"></sup>majesty.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13613AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13613AA\"></sup>“If I have made gold my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13613AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13613AB\"></sup>trustor called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13613AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13613AC\"></sup>fine gold my confidence,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>if I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13614AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13614AD\"></sup>rejoiced because my wealth was abundantor because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13614AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13614AE\"></sup>my hand had found much,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13615AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13615AF\"></sup>if I have looked at the sun when it shone,or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13615AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13615AG\"></sup>the moon moving in splendor,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>and my heart has been secretly enticed,and my mouth has kissed my hand,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>this also would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13617AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13617AH\"></sup>an iniquity to be punished by the judges,for I would have been false to God above.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“If I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13618AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13618AI\"></sup>rejoiced at the ruin of him who hated me,or exulted when evil overtook him",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>(<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13619AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13619AJ\"></sup>I have not let my mouth sinby asking for his life with a curse),",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>if the men of my tent have not said,‘Who is there that has not been filled with his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13620AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13620AK\"></sup>meat?’",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>(<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13621AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13621AL\"></sup>the sojourner has not lodged in the street;I have opened my doors to the traveler),",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>if I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13622AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13622AM\"></sup>have concealed my transgressions <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13622AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13622AN\"></sup>as others doby hiding my iniquity in my heart,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>because I stood in great fear of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13623AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13623AO\"></sup>the multitude,and the contempt of families terrified me,so that I kept silence, and did not go out of doors—",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Oh, that I had one to hear me!(Here is my signature! Let the Almighty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13624AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13624AP\"></sup>answer me!)Oh, that I had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13624AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13624AQ\"></sup>the indictment written by my adversary!",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Surely I would carry it on my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13625AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13625AR\"></sup>shoulder;I would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13625AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13625AS\"></sup>bind it on me as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13625AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13625AT\"></sup>a crown;",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>I would give him an account of all my steps;like a prince I would approach him.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>“If my land has cried out against meand its furrows have wept together,",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13628AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13628AU\"></sup>if I have eaten its yield without paymentand made its owners <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13628AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13628AV\"></sup>breathe their last,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13629AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13629AW\"></sup>thorns grow instead of wheat,and foul weeds instead of barley.”The words of Job are ended."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>So these three men ceased to answer Job, because he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13630A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13630A\"></sup>righteous in his own eyes.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then Elihu the son of Barachel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13631B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13631B\"></sup>the Buzite, of the family of Ram, burned with anger. He burned with anger at Job because he justified himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13631C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13631C\"></sup>rather than God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He burned with anger also at Job's three friends because they had found no answer, although they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13632D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13632D\"></sup>declared Job to be in the wrong.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now Elihu had waited to speak to Job because they were older than he.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And when Elihu saw that there was no answer in the mouth of these three men, he burned with anger.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And Elihu the son of Barachel the Buzite answered and said:“I am young in years,and you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13635E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13635E\"></sup>aged;therefore I was timid and afraidto declare my opinion to you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I said, ‘Let days speak,and many years teach wisdom.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13637F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13637F\"></sup>the spirit in man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13637G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13637G\"></sup>the breath of the Almighty, that makes him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13637H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13637H\"></sup>understand.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13638I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13638I\"></sup>It is not the old who are wise,nor the aged who understand what is right.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Therefore I say, ‘Listen to me;let me also declare my opinion.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Behold, I waited for your words,I listened for your wise sayings,while you searched out what to say.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I gave you my attention,and, behold, there was none among you who refuted Jobor who answered his words.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Beware <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13642J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13642J\"></sup>lest you say, ‘We have found wisdom;God may vanquish him, not a man.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He has not directed his words against me,and I will not answer him with your speeches.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“They are dismayed; they answer no more;they have not a word to say.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And shall I wait, because they do not speak,because they stand there, and answer no more?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I also will answer with my share;I also will declare my opinion.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For I am full of words;the spirit within me constrains me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Behold, my belly is like wine that has no vent;like new <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13648K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13648K\"></sup>wineskins ready to burst.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13649L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13649L\"></sup>I must speak, that I may find <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13649M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13649M\"></sup>relief;I must open my lips and answer.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13650N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13650N\"></sup>show partiality to any manor use flattery toward any person.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For I do not know how to flatter,else my Maker would soon take me away."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>“But now, hear my speech, O Job,and listen to all my words.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Behold, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13653A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13653A\"></sup>open my mouth;the tongue in my mouth speaks.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>My words declare the uprightness of my heart,and what my lips know they speak sincerely.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13655B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13655B\"></sup>The Spirit of God has made me,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13655C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13655C\"></sup>the breath of the Almighty gives me life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13656D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13656D\"></sup>Answer me, if you can;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13656E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13656E\"></sup>set your words in order before me; take your stand.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Behold, I am toward God as you are;I too was pinched off from a piece of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13657F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13657F\"></sup>clay.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Behold, no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13658G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13658G\"></sup>fear of me need terrify you;my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13658H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13658H\"></sup>pressure will not be heavy upon you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Surely you have spoken in my ears,and I have heard the sound of your words.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You say, ‘I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13660I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13660I\"></sup>pure, without <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13660J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13660J\"></sup>transgression;I am clean, and there is no iniquity in me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Behold, he finds occasions against me,he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13661K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13661K\"></sup>counts me as his enemy,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13662L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13662L\"></sup>puts my feet in the stocksand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13662M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13662M\"></sup>watches all my paths.’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Behold, in this you are not right. I will answer you,for God is greater than man.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Why do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13664N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13664N\"></sup>contend against him,saying, ‘He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13664O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13664O\"></sup>will answer none of man's words’?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13665P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13665P\"></sup>speaks in one way,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13665Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13665Q\"></sup>and in two, though man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13665R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13665R\"></sup>does not perceive it.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13666S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13666S\"></sup>a dream, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13666T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13666T\"></sup>a vision of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13666U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13666U\"></sup>the night,when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13666V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13666V\"></sup>deep sleep falls on men,while they slumber on their beds,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>then he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13667W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13667W\"></sup>opens the ears of menand terrifies them with warnings,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>that he may turn man aside from his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13668X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13668X\"></sup>deedand conceal pride from a man;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>he keeps back his soul from the pit,his life from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13669Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13669Y\"></sup>perishing by the sword.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Man is also rebuked with pain on his bedand with continual strife in his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13670Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13670Z\"></sup>bones,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>so that his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13671AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13671AA\"></sup>life loathes bread,and his appetite <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13671AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13671AB\"></sup>the choicest food.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>His flesh is so wasted away that it cannot be seen,and his bones that were not seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13672AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13672AC\"></sup>stick out.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>His soul draws near <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13673AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13673AD\"></sup>the pit,and his life to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13673AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13673AE\"></sup>those who bring death.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>If there be for him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13674AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13674AF\"></sup>an angel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13674AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13674AG\"></sup>a mediator, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13674AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13674AH\"></sup>one of the thousand,to declare to man what is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13674AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13674AI\"></sup>right for him,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and he is merciful to him, and says,‘Deliver him from going down into the pit;I have found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13675AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13675AJ\"></sup>a ransom;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>let his flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13676AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13676AK\"></sup>become fresh with youth;let him return to the days of his youthful vigor’;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>then man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13677AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13677AL\"></sup>prays to God, and he accepts him;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13677AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13677AM\"></sup>sees his face with a shout of joy,and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13677AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13677AN\"></sup>restores to man his righteousness.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>He sings before men and says:‘I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13678AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13678AO\"></sup>sinned and perverted what was right,and it was not repaid to me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>He has redeemed my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13679AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13679AP\"></sup>soul from going down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13679AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13679AQ\"></sup>into the pit,and my life shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13679AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13679AR\"></sup>look upon the light.’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Behold, God does all these things,twice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13680AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13680AS\"></sup>three times, with a man,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>to bring back his soul from the pit,that he may be lighted with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13681AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13681AT\"></sup>the light of life.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Pay attention, O Job, listen to me;be silent, and I will speak.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>If you have any words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13683AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13683AU\"></sup>answer me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13683AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13683AV\"></sup>speak, for I desire to justify you.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>If not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13684AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13684AW\"></sup>listen to me;be silent, and I will teach you wisdom.”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>Then Elihu answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Hear my words, you wise men,and give ear to me, you who know;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13687A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13687A\"></sup>the ear tests wordsas the palate tastes food.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Let us choose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13688B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13688B\"></sup>what is right;let us know among ourselves what is good.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For Job has said, ‘I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13689C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13689C\"></sup>in the right,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13689D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13689D\"></sup>God has taken away my right;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>in spite of my right I am counted a liar;my wound is incurable, though I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13690E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13690E\"></sup>without transgression.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>What man is like Job,who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13691F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13691F\"></sup>drinks up scoffing like water,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>who travels in company with evildoersand walks <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13692G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13692G\"></sup>with wicked men?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13693H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13693H\"></sup>he has said, ‘It profits a man nothingthat he should take delight in God.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Therefore, hear me, you men of understanding:far be it from God that he should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13694I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13694I\"></sup>do wickedness,and from the Almighty that he should do wrong.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13695J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13695J\"></sup>the work of a man he will repay him,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13695K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13695K\"></sup>according to his ways he will make it befall him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Of a truth, God will not do wickedly,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13696L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13696L\"></sup>the Almighty will not pervert justice.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Who gave him charge over the earth,and who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13697M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13697M\"></sup>laid on him the whole world?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If he should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13698N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13698N\"></sup>set his heart to itand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13698O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13698O\"></sup>gather to himself his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13698P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13698P\"></sup>spirit and his breath,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>all flesh would perish together,and man would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13699Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13699Q\"></sup>return to dust.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“If you have understanding, hear this;listen to what I say.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13701R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13701R\"></sup>Shall one who hates justice govern?Will you condemn him who is righteous and mighty,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13702S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13702S\"></sup>says to a king, ‘Worthless one,’and to nobles, ‘Wicked man,’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13703T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13703T\"></sup>shows no partiality to princes,nor regards the rich <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13703U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13703U\"></sup>more than the poor,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13703V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13703V\"></sup>they are all the work of his hands?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In a moment <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13704W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13704W\"></sup>they die;at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13704X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13704X\"></sup>midnight the people are shaken and pass away,and the mighty are taken away by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13704Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13704Y\"></sup>no human hand.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“For his eyes are on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13705Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13705Z\"></sup>the ways of a man,and he sees all his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13705AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13705AA\"></sup>steps.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>There is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13706AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13706AB\"></sup>gloom or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13706AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13706AC\"></sup>deep darknesswhere evildoers may hide themselves.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For God has no need to consider a man further,that he should go before God in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13707AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13707AD\"></sup>judgment.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13708AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13708AE\"></sup>shatters the mighty without investigationand sets <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13708AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13708AF\"></sup>others in their place.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Thus, knowing their works,he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13709AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13709AG\"></sup>overturns them in the night, and they are crushed.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He strikes them for their wickednessin a place for all to see,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>because they turned aside from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13711AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13711AH\"></sup>following himand had no regard for any of his ways,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>so that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13712AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13712AI\"></sup>caused the cry of the poor to come to him,and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13712AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13712AJ\"></sup>heard the cry of the afflicted—",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>When he is quiet, who can condemn?When he hides his face, who can behold him,whether it be a nation or a man?—",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>that a godless man should not reign,that he should not ensnare the people.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“For has anyone said to God,‘I have borne punishment; I will not offend any more;",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13716AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13716AK\"></sup>teach me what I do not see;if I have done iniquity, I will do it no more’?",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Will he then make repayment to suit you,because you reject it?For you must choose, and not I;therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13717AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13717AL\"></sup>declare what you know.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Men of understanding will say to me,and the wise man who hears me will say:",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>‘Job <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13719AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13719AM\"></sup>speaks without knowledge;his words are without insight.’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Would that Job were tried to the end,because he answers like wicked men.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For he adds rebellion to his sin;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13721AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13721AN\"></sup>claps his hands among usand multiplies his words against God.”"
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span>And Elihu answered and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Do you think this to be just?Do you say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13723A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13723A\"></sup>‘It is my right before God,’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>that you ask, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13724B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13724B\"></sup>‘What advantage have I?How am I better off than if I had sinned?’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will answer youand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13725C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13725C\"></sup>your friends with you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13726D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13726D\"></sup>Look at the heavens, and see;and behold the clouds, which are higher than you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If you have sinned, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13727E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13727E\"></sup>what do you accomplish against him?And if your transgressions are multiplied, what do you do to him?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13728F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13728F\"></sup>If you are righteous, what do you give to him?Or what does he receive from your hand?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Your wickedness concerns a man like yourself,and your righteousness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13729G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13729G\"></sup>a son of man.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Because of the multitude of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13730H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13730H\"></sup>oppressions people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13730I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13730I\"></sup>cry out;they call for help because of the arm of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13730J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13730J\"></sup>the mighty.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But none says, ‘Where is God my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13731K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13731K\"></sup>Maker,who gives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13731L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13731L\"></sup>songs in the night,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>who teaches us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13732M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13732M\"></sup>more than the beasts of the earthand makes us wiser than the birds of the heavens?’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>There they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13733N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13733N\"></sup>cry out, but he does not answer,because of the pride of evil men.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Surely God does not hear an empty cry,nor does the Almighty regard it.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>How much less when you say that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13735O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13735O\"></sup>do not see him,that the case is before him, and you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13735P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13735P\"></sup>waiting for him!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And now, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13736Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13736Q\"></sup>his anger does not punish,and he does not take much note of transgression,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Job opens his mouth in empty talk;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13737R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13737R\"></sup>multiplies words <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13737S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13737S\"></sup>without knowledge.”"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span>And Elihu continued, and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Bear with me a little, and I will show you,for I have yet something to say on God's behalf.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I will get my knowledge from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13740A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13740A\"></sup>afarand ascribe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13740B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13740B\"></sup>righteousness to my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13740C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13740C\"></sup>Maker.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For truly my words are not false;one who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13741D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13741D\"></sup>perfect in knowledge is with you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Behold, God is mighty, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13742E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13742E\"></sup>does not despise any;he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13742F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13742F\"></sup>mighty in strength of understanding.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He does not keep the wicked alive,but gives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13743G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13743G\"></sup>the afflicted their right.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He does not withdraw his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13744H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13744H\"></sup>eyes from the righteous,but with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13744I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13744I\"></sup>kings on the thronehe sets them forever, and they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13744J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13744J\"></sup>exalted.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And if they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13745K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13745K\"></sup>bound in chainsand caught in the cords of affliction,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>then he declares to them their workand their transgressions, that they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13746L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13746L\"></sup>behaving arrogantly.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13747M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13747M\"></sup>opens their ears to instructionand commands that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13747N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13747N\"></sup>return from iniquity.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13748O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13748O\"></sup>If they listen and serve him,they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13748P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13748P\"></sup>complete their days in prosperity,and their years in pleasantness.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But if they do not listen, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13749Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13749Q\"></sup>perish by the swordand die <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13749R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13749R\"></sup>without knowledge.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13750S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13750S\"></sup>godless in heart cherish anger;they do not cry for help when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13750T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13750T\"></sup>binds them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13751U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13751U\"></sup>die in youth,and their life ends among the cult prostitutes.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He delivers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13752V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13752V\"></sup>the afflicted by their afflictionand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13752W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13752W\"></sup>opens their ear by adversity.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He also allured you out of distressinto <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13753X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13753X\"></sup>a broad place where there was no cramping,and what was set on your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13753Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13753Y\"></sup>table was full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13753Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13753Z\"></sup>fatness.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“But you are full of the judgment on the wicked;judgment and justice seize you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Beware lest wrath entice you into scoffing,and let not the greatness of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13755AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13755AA\"></sup>the ransom turn you aside.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Will your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13756AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13756AB\"></sup>cry for help avail to keep you from distress,or all the force of your strength?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do not long for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13757AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13757AC\"></sup>the night,when peoples vanish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13757AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13757AD\"></sup>in their place.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Take care; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13758AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13758AE\"></sup>do not turn to iniquity,for this you have chosen rather than affliction.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Behold, God is exalted in his power;who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13759AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13759AF\"></sup>a teacher like him?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13760AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13760AG\"></sup>prescribed for him his way,or who can say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13760AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13760AH\"></sup>‘You have done wrong’?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Remember to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13761AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13761AI\"></sup>extol his work,of which men have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13761AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13761AJ\"></sup>sung.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>All mankind has looked on it;man beholds it from afar.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Behold, God is great, and we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13763AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13763AK\"></sup>know him not;the number of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13763AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13763AL\"></sup>years is unsearchable.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For he draws up the drops of water;they distill his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13764AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13764AM\"></sup>mist in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13764AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13764AN\"></sup>rain,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13765AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13765AO\"></sup>the skies pour downand drop on mankind abundantly.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Can anyone understand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13766AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13766AP\"></sup>the spreading of the clouds,the thunderings of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13766AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13766AQ\"></sup>pavilion?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Behold, he scatters his lightning about himand covers the roots of the sea.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>For by these he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13768AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13768AR\"></sup>judges peoples;he gives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13768AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13768AS\"></sup>food in abundance.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>He covers his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13769AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13769AT\"></sup>hands with the lightningand commands it to strike the mark.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Its crashing declares his presence;the cattle also declare that he rises."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span>“At this also my heart tremblesand leaps out of its place.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Keep listening to the thunder of his voiceand the rumbling that comes from his mouth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Under the whole heaven he lets it go,and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13773A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13773A\"></sup>lightning to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13773B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13773B\"></sup>corners of the earth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>After it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13774C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13774C\"></sup>his voice roars;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13774D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13774D\"></sup>he thunders with his majestic voice,and he does not restrain the lightnings when his voice is heard.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>God thunders wondrously with his voice;he does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13775E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13775E\"></sup>great things that we cannot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13775F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13775F\"></sup>comprehend.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13776G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13776G\"></sup>the snow he says, ‘Fall on the earth,’likewise to the downpour, his mighty downpour.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13777H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13777H\"></sup>seals up the hand of every man,that all men whom he made may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13777I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13777I\"></sup>know it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the beasts go into their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13778J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13778J\"></sup>lairs,and remain in their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13778K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13778K\"></sup>dens.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13779L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13779L\"></sup>its chamber <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13779M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13779M\"></sup>comes the whirlwind,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13779N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13779N\"></sup>cold from the scattering winds.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>By the breath of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13780O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13780O\"></sup>ice is given,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13780P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13780P\"></sup>the broad waters are frozen fast.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He loads the thick cloud with moisture;the clouds scatter his lightning.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13782Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13782Q\"></sup>turn around and around by his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13782R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13782R\"></sup>guidance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13782S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13782S\"></sup>to accomplish all that he commands themon the face of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13782T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13782T\"></sup>the habitable world.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Whether for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13783U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13783U\"></sup>correction or for his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13783V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13783V\"></sup>landor for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13783W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13783W\"></sup>love, he causes it to happen.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Hear this, O Job;stop and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13784X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13784X\"></sup>consider the wondrous works of God.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Do you know how God lays his command upon themand causes the lightning of his cloud to shine?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Do you know the balancings of the clouds,the wondrous works of him who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13786Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13786Y\"></sup>perfect in knowledge,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>you whose garments are hotwhen the earth is still because of the south wind?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Can you, like him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13788Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13788Z\"></sup>spread out the skies,hard as a cast metal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13788AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13788AA\"></sup>mirror?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Teach us what we shall say to him;we cannot draw up our case because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13789AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13789AB\"></sup>darkness.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Shall it be told him that I would speak?Did a man ever wish that he would be swallowed up?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“And now no one looks on the lightwhen it is bright in the skies,when the wind has passed and cleared them.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Out of the north comes golden splendor;God is clothed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13792AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13792AC\"></sup>awesome majesty.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The Almighty—we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13793AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13793AD\"></sup>cannot find him;he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13793AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13793AE\"></sup>great in power;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13793AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13793AF\"></sup>justice and abundant righteousness he will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13793AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13793AG\"></sup>violate.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13794AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13794AH\"></sup>fear him;he does not regard any who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13794AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13794AI\"></sup>wise in their own conceit.”"
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13795A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13795A\"></sup>answered Job out of the whirlwind and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Who is this that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13796B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13796B\"></sup>darkens counsel by words <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13796C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13796C\"></sup>without knowledge?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13797D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13797D\"></sup>Dress for action like a man;I will question you, and you make it known to me.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Where were you when I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13798E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13798E\"></sup>laid the foundation of the earth?Tell me, if you have understanding.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Who determined its measurements—surely you know!Or who stretched the line upon it?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On what were its bases sunk,or who laid its cornerstone,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>when the morning stars <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13801F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13801F\"></sup>sang togetherand all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13801G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13801G\"></sup>the sons of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13801H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13801H\"></sup>shouted for joy?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Or who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13802I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13802I\"></sup>shut in the sea with doorswhen it burst out from the womb,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>when I made clouds its garmentand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13803J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13803J\"></sup>thick darkness its swaddling band,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and prescribed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13804K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13804K\"></sup>limits for itand set bars and doors,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and said, ‘Thus far shall you come, and no farther,and here shall your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13805L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13805L\"></sup>proud waves be stayed’?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13806M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13806M\"></sup>commanded the morning since your days began,and caused the dawn to know its place,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>that it might take hold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13807N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13807N\"></sup>the skirts of the earth,and the wicked be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13807O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13807O\"></sup>shaken out of it?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>It is changed like clay under the seal,and its features stand out like a garment.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>From the wicked their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13809P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13809P\"></sup>light is withheld,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13809Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13809Q\"></sup>their uplifted arm is broken.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13810R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13810R\"></sup>entered into the springs of the sea,or walked in the recesses of the deep?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13811S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13811S\"></sup>the gates of death been revealed to you,or have you seen the gates of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13811T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13811T\"></sup>deep darkness?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Have you comprehended the expanse of the earth?Declare, if you know all this.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Where is the way to the dwelling of light,and where is the place of darkness,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>that you may take it to its territoryand that you may discern <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13814U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13814U\"></sup>the paths to its home?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You know, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13815V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13815V\"></sup>you were born then,and the number of your days is great!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Have you entered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13816W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13816W\"></sup>the storehouses of the snow,or have you seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13816X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13816X\"></sup>the storehouses of the hail,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>which I have reserved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13817Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13817Y\"></sup>for the time of trouble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13817Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13817Z\"></sup>for the day of battle and war?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>What is the way to the place where the light is distributed,or where the east wind is scattered upon the earth?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Who has cleft a channel for the torrents of rainand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13819AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13819AA\"></sup>a way for the thunderbolt,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>to bring rain on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13820AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13820AB\"></sup>a land where no man is,on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13820AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13820AC\"></sup>the desert in which there is no man,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>to satisfy the waste and desolate land,and to make the ground sprout with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13821AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13821AD\"></sup>grass?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13822AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13822AE\"></sup>the rain a father,or who has begotten the drops of dew?",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>From whose womb did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13823AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13823AF\"></sup>the ice come forth,and who has given birth to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13823AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13823AG\"></sup>the frost of heaven?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The waters become hard like stone,and the face of the deep is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13824AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13824AH\"></sup>frozen.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Can you bind the chains of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13825AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13825AI\"></sup>the Pleiadesor loose the cords of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13825AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13825AJ\"></sup>Orion?",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Can you lead forth the Mazzaroth in their season,or can you guide <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13826AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13826AK\"></sup>the Bear with its children?",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Do you know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13827AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13827AL\"></sup>the ordinances of the heavens?Can you establish their rule on the earth?",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Can you lift up your voice to the clouds,that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13828AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13828AM\"></sup>a flood of waters may cover you?",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Can you send forth lightnings, that they may goand say to you, ‘Here we are’?",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13830AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13830AN\"></sup>put wisdom in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13830AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13830AO\"></sup>the inward partsor given understanding to the mind?",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Who can number the clouds by wisdom?Or who can tilt the waterskins of the heavens,",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>when the dust runs into a massand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13832AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13832AP\"></sup>the clods stick fast together?",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“Can you hunt the prey for the lion,or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13833AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13833AQ\"></sup>satisfy the appetite of the young lions,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>when they crouch in their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13834AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13834AR\"></sup>densor lie in wait <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13834AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13834AS\"></sup>in their thicket?",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Who provides for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13835AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13835AT\"></sup>the raven its prey,when its young ones cry to God for help,and wander about for lack of food?"
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">39 </span>“Do you know when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13836A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13836A\"></sup>the mountain goats give birth?Do you observe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13836B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13836B\"></sup>the calving of the does?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Can you number the months that they fulfill,and do you know the time when they give birth,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>when they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13838C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13838C\"></sup>crouch, bring forth their offspring,and are delivered of their young?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Their young ones become strong; they grow up in the open;they go out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13839D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13839D\"></sup>do not return to them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Who has let the wild donkey go free?Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13840E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13840E\"></sup>loosed the bonds of the swift donkey,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>to whom I have given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13841F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13841F\"></sup>the arid plain for his homeand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13841G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13841G\"></sup>the salt land for his dwelling place?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He scorns the tumult of the city;he hears not the shouts of the driver.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He ranges the mountains as his pasture,and he searches after every green thing.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13844H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13844H\"></sup>the wild ox willing to serve you?Will he spend the night at your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13844I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13844I\"></sup>manger?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Can you bind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13845J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13845J\"></sup>him in the furrow with ropes,or will he harrow the valleys after you?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Will you depend on him because his strength is great,and will you leave to him your labor?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Do you have faith in him that he will return your grainand gather it to your threshing floor?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The wings of the ostrich wave proudly,but are they the pinions and plumage of love?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For she leaves her eggs to the earthand lets them be warmed on the ground,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>forgetting that a foot may crush themand that the wild beast may trample them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13851K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13851K\"></sup>deals cruelly with her young, as if they were not hers;though her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13851L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13851L\"></sup>labor be in vain, yet she has no fear,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>because God has made her forget wisdomand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13852M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13852M\"></sup>given her no share in understanding.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When she rouses herself to flee,she laughs at the horse and his rider.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Do you give the horse his might?Do you clothe his neck with a mane?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do you make him leap like the locust?His majestic <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13855N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13855N\"></sup>snorting is terrifying.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He paws in the valley and exults in his strength;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13856O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13856O\"></sup>goes out to meet the weapons.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He laughs at fear and is not dismayed;he does not turn back from the sword.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Upon him rattle the quiver,the flashing spear, and the javelin.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>With fierceness and rage he swallows the ground;he cannot stand still at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13859P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13859P\"></sup>the sound of the trumpet.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When the trumpet sounds, he says ‘Aha!’He smells the battle from afar,the thunder of the captains, and the shouting.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Is it by your understanding that the hawk soarsand spreads his wings toward the south?",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Is it at your command that the eagle mounts upand makes his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13862Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13862Q\"></sup>nest on high?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>On the rock he dwells and makes his home,on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13863R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13863R\"></sup>the rocky crag and stronghold.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>From there he spies out the prey;his eyes behold it from far away.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>His young ones suck up blood,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13865S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13865S\"></sup>where the slain are, there is he.”"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13866A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13866A\"></sup>said to Job:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Shall a faultfinder <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13867B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13867B\"></sup>contend with the Almighty?He who argues with God, let him answer it.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then Job answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said:",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13869C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13869C\"></sup>of small account; what shall I answer you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13869D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13869D\"></sup>I lay my hand on my mouth.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I have spoken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13870E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13870E\"></sup>once, and I will not answer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13870F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13870F\"></sup>twice, but I will proceed no further.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13871G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13871G\"></sup>answered Job out of the whirlwind and said:",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13872H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13872H\"></sup>“Dress for action like a man;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13872I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13872I\"></sup>I will question you, and you make it known to me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Will you even put me in the wrong?Will you condemn me that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13873J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13873J\"></sup>you may be in the right?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13874K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13874K\"></sup>an arm like God,and can you thunder with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13874L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13874L\"></sup>a voice like his?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Adorn yourself with majesty and dignity;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13875M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13875M\"></sup>clothe yourself with glory and splendor.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Pour out the overflowings of your anger,and look on everyone who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13876N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13876N\"></sup>proud and abase him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Look on everyone who is proud and bring him lowand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13877O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13877O\"></sup>tread down the wicked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13877P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13877P\"></sup>where they stand.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13878Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13878Q\"></sup>Hide them all in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13878R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13878R\"></sup>the dust together;bind their faces in the world below.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then will I also acknowledge to youthat your own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13879S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13879S\"></sup>right hand can save you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Behold, Behemoth,which I made as I made you;he eats <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13880T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13880T\"></sup>grass like an ox.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Behold, his strength in his loins,and his power in the muscles of his belly.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He makes his tail stiff like a cedar;the sinews of his thighs are knit together.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>His bones are tubes of bronze,his limbs like bars of iron.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13884U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13884U\"></sup>the first of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13884V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13884V\"></sup>the works of God;let him who made him bring near his sword!",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For the mountains yield food for himwhere all the wild beasts play.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Under the lotus plants he lies,in the shelter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13886W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13886W\"></sup>the reeds and in the marsh.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For his shade the lotus trees cover him;the willows of the brook surround him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Behold, if the river is turbulent he is not frightened;he is confident though Jordan rushes against his mouth.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Can one take him by his eyes,or pierce his nose with a snare?"
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span> “Can you draw out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13890A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13890A\"></sup>Leviathan with a fishhookor press down his tongue with a cord?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Can you put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13891B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13891B\"></sup>a rope in his noseor pierce his jaw with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13891C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13891C\"></sup>a hook?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Will he make many pleas to you?Will he speak to you soft words?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Will he make a covenant with youto take him for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13893D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13893D\"></sup>your servant forever?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Will you play with him as with a bird,or will you put him on a leash for your girls?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Will traders bargain over him?Will they divide him up among the merchants?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Can you fill his skin with harpoonsor his head with fishing spears?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Lay your hands on him;remember the battle—you will not do it again!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup> Behold, the hope of a man is false;he is laid low even at the sight of him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>No one is so fierce that he dares to stir him up.Who then is he who can stand before me?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13900E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13900E\"></sup>Who has first given to me, that I should repay him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13900F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13900F\"></sup>Whatever is under the whole heaven is mine.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I will not keep silence concerning his limbs,or his mighty strength, or his goodly frame.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Who can strip off his outer garment?Who would come near him with a bridle?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Who can open the doors of his face?Around his teeth is terror.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>His back is made of rows of shields,shut up closely as with a seal.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>One is so near to anotherthat no air can come between them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13906G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13906G\"></sup>joined one to another;they clasp each other and cannot be separated.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>His sneezings flash forth light,and his eyes are like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13907H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13907H\"></sup>the eyelids of the dawn.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Out of his mouth go flaming torches;sparks of fire leap forth.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Out of his nostrils comes forth smoke,as from a boiling pot and burning rushes.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>His breath <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13910I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13910I\"></sup>kindles coals,and a flame comes forth from his mouth.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>In his neck abides strength,and terror dances before him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The folds of his flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13912J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13912J\"></sup>stick together,firmly cast on him and immovable.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>His heart is hard as a stone,hard as the lower millstone.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When he raises himself up, the mighty are afraid;at the crashing they are beside themselves.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Though the sword reaches him, it does not avail,nor the spear, the dart, or the javelin.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He counts iron as straw,and bronze as rotten wood.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The arrow cannot make him flee;for him, sling stones are turned to stubble.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Clubs are counted as stubble;he laughs at the rattle of javelins.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>His underparts are like sharp <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13919K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13919K\"></sup>potsherds;he spreads himself like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13919L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13919L\"></sup>a threshing sledge on the mire.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>He makes the deep boil like a pot;he makes the sea like a pot of ointment.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Behind him he leaves a shining wake;one would think the deep to be white-haired.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13922M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13922M\"></sup>On earth there is not his like,a creature without fear.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>He sees everything that is high;he is king over all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13923N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13923N\"></sup>sons of pride.”"
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span>Then Job answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I know that you can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13925A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13925A\"></sup>do all things,and that no purpose of yours can be thwarted.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13926B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13926B\"></sup>‘Who is this that hides counsel without knowledge?’Therefore I have uttered what I did not understand,things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13926C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13926C\"></sup>too wonderful for me, which I did not know.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>‘Hear, and I will speak;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13927D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13927D\"></sup>I will question you, and you make it known to me.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I had heard of you by the hearing of the ear,but now my eye sees you;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>therefore I despise myself,and repent in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13929E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13929E\"></sup>dust and ashes.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>After the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had spoken these words to Job, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Eliphaz <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13930F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13930F\"></sup>the Temanite: “My anger burns against you and against your two friends, for you have not spoken of me what is right, as my servant Job has.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now therefore take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13931G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13931G\"></sup>seven bulls and seven rams and go to my servant Job and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13931H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13931H\"></sup>offer up a burnt offering for yourselves. And my servant Job shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13931I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13931I\"></sup>pray for you, for I will accept his prayer not to deal with you according to your folly. For you have not spoken of me what is right, as my servant Job has.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13932J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13932J\"></sup>So Eliphaz the Temanite and Bildad the Shuhite and Zophar the Naamathite went and did what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had told them, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> accepted Job's prayer.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13933K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13933K\"></sup>restored the fortunes of Job, when he had prayed for his friends. And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave Job <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13933L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13933L\"></sup>twice as much as he had before.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then came to him all his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13934M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13934M\"></sup>brothers and sisters and all who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13934N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13934N\"></sup>known him before, and ate bread with him in his house. And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13934O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13934O\"></sup>showed him sympathy and comforted him for all the evil that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had brought upon him. And each of them gave him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13934P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13934P\"></sup>a piece of money and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13934Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13934Q\"></sup>a ring of gold.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> blessed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13935R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13935R\"></sup>the latter days of Job more than his beginning. And he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13935S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13935S\"></sup>14,000 sheep, 6,000 camels, 1,000 yoke of oxen, and 1,000 female donkeys.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He had also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13936T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13936T\"></sup>seven sons and three daughters.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And he called the name of the first daughter Jemimah, and the name of the second Keziah, and the name of the third Keren-happuch.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And in all the land there were no women so beautiful as Job's daughters. And their father gave them an inheritance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13938U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13938U\"></sup>among their brothers.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And after this Job lived 140 years, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13939V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13939V\"></sup>saw his sons, and his sons' sons, four generations.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And Job died, an old man, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-13940W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-13940W\"></sup>full of days."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;